quran[842]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,(Ndifunga) ngezo ngelosi zikreliswe ngokwemigca
  37,2,Nangezo ziqhuba amafu
  37,3,Nangezo zicengceleza umyalezo (wesiTyhilelo)
  37,4,Inene uThixo wakho Mnye
  37,5,"INkosi yamazulu nomhlaba noko kungaphakathi kwawo, EkwayiNkosi yeeMpumalanga"
  37,6,Inene Thina Silihombisile izulu elikufutshane ngeenkwenkwezi zokuhombisa
  37,7,Ezikwalukhuselo ngokuchasene naye nawuphi na uShaytân ongumvukeli
  37,8,Ukuze (bangachwechwi) baye kuphulaphula intlanganiso ebekekileyo (yeengelosi) yaye (aba Sathana) baxulutywa (ngamadangatya omlilo) macala onke (abazama ukuvela ngakuwo)
  37,9,Bagxothwe; yaye abakufumanayo kukohlwaywa rhoqo
  37,10,"Ngaphandle kwabo baxhwila (amazwi athile) ngobusela, kodwa nabo bayaleqwa ngezikhuni ezivuthayo, (ezikhanya) ngokugqobhozelayo"
  37,11,"Khawubabuze (Muhammad) okukuba ingaba ngabo na abayeyona ndalo iqinileyo okanye yenye na (indalo enjengamazulu nomhlaba neentaba) eSazidalayo? Inene, bona Sabadala ngodongwe oluncangathi"
  37,12,Ewe kakade (wena Muhammad) uye wamangaliseka (yindelelo yabo) xa bebekugculela (wena ne’Kur’ân)
  37,13,Naxa bekhunjuzwa (ngoAllâh) abahoyi
  37,14,Naxa bebona umqondiso bayawugculela
  37,15,"Bade bathi: “Asinto yimbi le ngaphandle kokuba ngumlingo ocacileyo"
  37,16,Ingaba xa sifile sele siluthuli namathambo siza kuphinda sivuswe kwakhona
  37,17,Ndawonye noobawo bethu bamandulo?”
  37,18,"Yithi wena (Muhammad): “Ewe, yaye niya kuhlaziswa.”"
  37,19,"Iya kuba sisikhalo esinye (seXilongo), yabonani! Baya kuthi ndlaa (amehlo besoyika)"
  37,20,"Baya\tkuthi:\t“Yeha\tkuthi!\tLe\tyiyo\t(ngenene)\tiMini yembuyekezo!”"
  37,21,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Yiyo le ke iMini yoMgwebo enanidla ngokuyiphika.”"
  37,22,"(Kuya kuthiwa kwiingelosi): “Qokelelani ndaweninye bonke abo benza ubugwenxa, bedibene noogxa babo (ooSathana abangamademon) nezo nto2 babedla ngokuzikhonza"
  37,23,"Endaweni ka-Allâh, nibakhokelele endleleni eya edangatyeni loMlilo (isiHogo)"
  37,24,"Kodwa khanibamise, kuba inene bona kufuneka bebuziwe"
  37,25,"Yintoni ngani, yini na ebangela ukuba ningancedisani (njengoko nanincedisana emhlabeni)"
  37,26,"Nakanye, bona baya kusuka bazinikezele"
  37,27,"Ke kaloku baya kujika bajongane , babuzane"
  37,28,"Baya kuthi: “Nini (booSathana) ababedla ngokuza kuthi nivela ngasekunene kwethu (nisilahlekise ngokusenzela ntle indlela eya ekwenzeni ubutshinga)”"
  37,29,"Baya kuphendula ke bona: “Unotshe! Nini ngokwenu eningazanga nikholwe"
  37,30,"Ngapha koko thina sasingenagunya phezu kwenu. Nakanye, nina nasuka naba ngabagabadeli"
  37,31,"“Ngoku ke iLizwi leNkosi yethu liyathetheleka ngokuchasene nathi, mayela nokuba singcamle (isohlwayo)"
  37,32,"Ke\tngoko\tsanikhokelela\tekulahlekeni\tkuba\tnathi sasilahlekile.”"
  37,33,Inene ngaloo Mini baya kwabelana ngesohlwayo
  37,34,"Ngokwenene, leyo yindlela esiqubisana ngayo nabenzi bobubi"
  37,35,"Ke kaloku, xa kusithiwa kubo: “Akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle koAllâh,” bona bayazikhukhumalisa, (baphikise)"
  37,36,"Kananjalo bathi: “Siza kushiya oothixo bethu ngenxa yembongi ephambeneyo na"
  37,37,Nakanye! Yena (uMuhammad) ufike nenyaniso (i-Islam ne’Kur’ân) yaye yena uyabangqina abaThunywa (abangaphambili kunaye)
  37,38,Inene nina (bahedenindini) niza kusingcamla isohlwayo esibuhlungu
  37,39,Kananjalo aniyi kubuyekezwa nganto ngaphandle koko nanidla ngokukwenza
  37,40,Ngaphandle kwezicaka ezinyanisekileyo zika-Allâh
  37,41,Kwabo banjalo kuya kubakho umsindleko owaziwayo
  37,42,Iziqhamo yaye baya kuhlonipheka
  37,43,EMiyezweni yolonwabo
  37,44,Bejongene (behleli zava) ezitroneni
  37,45,Emacaleni abo kuya kuba kugqithiswa indebe yewayini elungileyo (ehlambulukileyo)
  37,46,Emhlophe nenencasa kwabayiselayo
  37,47,"Abayi kuva buhlungu apho nabubi, bengayi kuva kunxila nakuyotywa (apho)"
  37,48,"Kanti\temacaleni\tkwabo\tkuya\tkubakho\tabasetyhini, ababajezula ngamehlo abo amahle"
  37,49,"(Ababuthathaka,\tbenyulu)\tngokungengathi\tngamaqanda anonotshelweyo"
  37,50,Ke kaloku baya kujongana babuzane
  37,51,"Isithethi phakathi kwabo siya kuthi: “Ndandinomhlobo (ehlabathini)"
  37,52,"Owayedla ngokuthi (kum): “Ingaba wena ungomnye wabo bakholwayo (kuvuko lwasemva kokufa na)?”"
  37,53,"Esithi (kananjalo): “Ingaba xa sele sifile, siluthuli namathambo, siza kuvuswa ngenene samkeliswe umvuzo okanye isohlwayo kusini na?”"
  37,54,"Kwathiwa kuye: “Ungakhe ujonge phantsi na?”"
  37,55,Wajonga ke phantsi waza wambona (umhlobo lowo wakhe) esazulwini soMlilo
  37,56,"Wathi kuye: “Ndifunga ngoAllâh, inene wena waphantsela ukunditshabalalisa"
  37,57,"Ukuba ngaba kwakungekho ngenxa yoBabalo lweNkosi yam, inene le, ngendandibe ngomnye wabo batyhalelwa (eMlilweni).”"
  37,58,"(Ke kaloku abemi basePaladesi baya kuthi): Ingaba asizi kuphinda sife kwakhona na"
  37,59,"Ngaphandle kokufa kwethu okokuqala, kananjalo ingaba asizi kohlwaywa na (emva kokungena kwethu eMyezweni?)”"
  37,60,"Inene, le yimpumelelo enkulu"
  37,61,Ngenxa yokunjengoku abasebenzi (bokulungileyo) mabasebenze
  37,62,Ingaba yiPaladesi na elungileyo okanye ngumthi weZa’kkum (umthi ombi osesihogweni)
  37,63,Inene wona siwenze waba yintshutshiso kubenzi bobubi
  37,64,Inene wona ngumthi ohluma ngaphantsi koMlilo wesiHogo
  37,65,Amagaqa eziqhamo zawo anjengeentloko zamashayâtîn (amademon)
  37,66,Inene baza kutyiswa (ezo ziqhamo) bazalise izisu zabo ngazo
  37,67,"Baze phezu koko banikwe amanzi abilayo, ukuba basele khona ukuze ibe ngumxube (wamanzi eZa’kkum ngaphakathi eziswini zabo)"
  37,68,Kuze emva koko inene ibe kukubuyiselwa kwabo eMlilweni wesiHogo odwanguzayo
  37,69,Inene bona bafumana ookhokho babo besendleleni egwenxa
  37,70,Ngoko ke nabo balandela ezinyaweni zabo
  37,71,Yaye inene uninzi lwabantu bakudala ababandulelayo babelahlekile
  37,72,"Kananjalo\tThina\tSasithumela\tabalumkisi\t(abaprofeti) phakathi kwabo"
  37,73,Khangelakeukubasabanjaninaisiphelosabobabelunyukisiwe (abamamela)
  37,74,Ngaphandle kwezicaka ezikhethiweyo zika-Allâh
  37,75,"Kananjalo uNûh wathandaza kuThi, yaye Thina Singabona balungileyo ukuphendula (imithandazo)"
  37,76,Ke kaloku Samsindisa yena nosapho lwakhe embandezelweni enkulu (yokurhaxwa ngamanzi)
  37,77,Kanti nenzala yakhe yona Sayenza ukuba ibe ngabasindileyo
  37,78,Saza Samshiyela (inkumbulo elungileyo) kwizizukulwana ezalandelayo emva koko
  37,79,Uxolo malube phezu koNûh emaphakadeni
  37,80,Siwavuza ngolo hlobo ke amalungisa
  37,81,"Inene, yena uNûh wayengomnye wabo babekholiwe kuThi"
  37,82,Kananjalo Sabatshonisa emanzini abanye
  37,83,Ke kaloku phakathi kwabo balandela indlela yakhe (uNûh) yaba nguIbrâhîm
  37,84,Wathi akuza eNkosini yakhe ngentliziyo ehlambulukileyo
  37,85,"Yabona; wathi kuyise nakubantu bakubo: “Yintoni na le niyinqulayo (apha)?”"
  37,86,“Ingaba ngoothixo bobuxoki na aba nifuna bona nina
  37,87,Kanti nicinga ntoni ngeNkosi uMlondolozi wamazwe?”
  37,88,Waza wakrwaqula ezinkwenkwezini
  37,89,"Wathi: “Inene mna ndigula (sisibetho3)”"
  37,90,Bahamba ke bamshiya (besoyika ukusulelwa sisifo eso)
  37,91,"Wabuyela yena kwizithixo zabo wathi: “Aniyi kutya na (kwiminikelo yamadini abekwe phambi kwenu?”)"
  37,92,Kuqhubeka ntoni kanye ngani ningathethi nje
  37,93,Waphethukela kuzo wazibetha ngesandla sakhe sokunene
  37,94,"Baza bona abakhonzi bezithixo, beza kuye ngokungxama"
  37,95,"Wathi yena (kubo): “Ingaba nina ninqula oko nikwenze (ngezandla zenu) na?”"
  37,96,Lo gama uAllâh Edale nina kunye noko nikwenzayo (kuzizithixo)!”
  37,97,"Bathi bona: “Makheleni isakhiwo (esiliziko uIbrâhîm), nize nimphose edangatyeni lomlilo!”"
  37,98,Baqulunqa iyelenqe elo ke kodwa Sasuka Sabenza bangabona bangaphantsi
  37,99,"Ke kaloku wathi yena (emva kokuba ehlanguliwe emlilweni): “InenemnandiyakuyaeNkosiniyam,Yiyo Eyakundikhokela"
  37,100,Nkosi yam ndiphe (inzala) eya kuba phakathi kwamalungisa.”
  37,101,Samnika iindaba ezilungileyo zomntwana oyinkwenkwe enomonde
  37,102,"Wathi unyana (wakhe lowo) esakuba emdala ngokwaneleyo ukuba ahambe naye, wathi kuye: “O nyana wam! Ndibone ephupheni ndixhela wena (njengedini lomnikelo kuAllah). Bona wena ke ukuba ucinga ntoni na!” Wathi yena: “O tata! Yenza oko ukuyalelweyo, ukuba uAllâh Uyavuma uya kundifumana ndingonyamezelayo.”"
  37,103,"Bathi ke besakuba bezinikele bobabini (phantsi kwentando ka-Allâh),Waba sele emlalise phantsi emqubudise ngebunzi lakhe (elungiselela ukumnqumla umqala)"
  37,104,"Samkhwaza: “Hini na Ibrâhîm"
  37,105,"Ulizalisekisile\tiphupha!”\tSiwavuza\tkanjalo\tke\tThina amalungisa"
  37,106,Olo yayilucikido lokwenene
  37,107,Samkhulula ngedini elikhulu (inkunzi yegusha)
  37,108,"Kananjalo\tyena\tsamshiyela\t(inkumbulo\telungileyo) kwizizukulwana ezisezayo"
  37,109,Uxolo malube kuIbrâhîm
  37,110,Siwavuza ngolo hlobo ke amalungisa
  37,111,Inene yena wayengomnye wabakhonzi beThu ababekholiwe
  37,112,Samnika iindaba ezivuyisayo zikaIs-hâ’k (uIsake)
  37,113,"Samsikelela yena noIs-hâ’k kodwa kwinzala yabo kukho abo benza okulungileyo, nabo bazona (imiphefumlo yabo) ngokuselubala"
  37,114,Kananjalo Senzela ubabalo uMûsâ noHârûn (uAron)
  37,115,Sabasindisa bona nabantu bakubo kwinkxwaleko enkulu
  37,116,"Sabanceda, khona ukuze babe noloyiso"
  37,117,Ke kaloku Sabanika isiBhalo esicacileyo
  37,118,Sabakhokelela eNdleleni ethe Tye
  37,119,"Sabashiyela\t(inkumbulo\telungileyo)\tkwizizukulwana ezisezayo"
  37,120,“Uxolo malube kuMûsâ noHârûn!”
  37,121,Sibavuza kanjalo ke Thina abenzi bokulungileyo
  37,122,Inene bona (uMûsâ noHârûn) babezizicaka zeThu ezibini ezikholwayo
  37,123,Kananjalo uIlyâs (uEliya) yayingomnye wabaThunywa
  37,124,"Xa wathi kubantu bakubo: “Aniyi kumoyika na uAllâh?”"
  37,125,Ingaba niza kubiza kuBhali na niyeke Oyena Mdali Wokwenene
  37,126,"uAllâh OyiNkosi yenu, OyiNkosi yooyihlo’mkhulu?”"
  37,127,"Kodwa basuka bamphikisa yena (uIlyâs)4, ngoko ke baza kuziswa ngaphambili (esohlwayweni)"
  37,128,Ngaphandle kwezicaka ezikhethiweyo zika-Allâh
  37,129,Yena Samshiyela (inkumbulo elungileyo) kwizizukulwana ezisezayo
  37,130,“Uxolo malube kuIlyâsiîn!”
  37,131,Sibavuza kanjalo keThina abenzi bokulungileyo
  37,132,Inene yena wayengomnye wezicaka zeThu ezikholiweyo
  37,133,Kanti noLût yayingomnye wabaThunywa
  37,134,Xa Samsindisayo yena nosapho lwakhe lonke
  37,135,Ngaphandle kwexhegokazi (umkakhe) elaba ngomnye wabo bashiyeka ngemva
  37,136,Sabatshabalalisa bonke abanye (bezixeko ezo iSodom neGomora)
  37,137,Inene nina nigqitha ngakubo (abo bafela apho) ekuseni
  37,138,Nasebusuku; ingaba aniyi kucingisisa na
  37,139,Kanti noYûnus wayengomnye wabaThunywa
  37,140,Xa wabalekela kwinqanawa eyayinomthwalo
  37,141,"Wavuma ke ukwenza amaqashiso, waza waba ngomnye wabo balahlekelwayo"
  37,142,Ke kaloku intlanzi enkulu yamginya njengoko wayenze isenzo esigxekekileyo
  37,143,Ukuba ngaba wayengazanga abe ngomnye wabo bazukisa uAllâh
  37,144,Inene yena wayeza kuhlala esiswini sentlanzi de kube yimini yoVuko
  37,145,Kodwa Samphosela elunxwemeni egula enjalo
  37,146,Ke kaloku Sahlumisa umthi womhlavuthwa phezu kwakhe (ngentla kwakhe)
  37,147,Kananjalo Samthumela kubantu abangamawaka aliwaka nangaphezulu kunoko
  37,148,Bakholwa ke; Saza Sabanika ulonwabo lokwethutyana
  37,149,"Ngoku ke khawubabuze (Muhammad): “Ingaba ziintombi5 (zodwa) na Enazo iNkosi yakho baze bona babe noonyana na?”"
  37,150,"Okanye\tmhlawumbi\t(bathi)\tSadala\tiingelosi\tzaba ngabasetyhini lo gama babebukele bona kusini na"
  37,151,Inene kungobuxoki babo le nto abahedeni besithi
  37,152,"“UAllâh Uzele”, bona ngamaxoki okwenene"
  37,153,Ingaba Yena Uzikhethele iintombi kusini na endaweni yoonyana
  37,154,Yintoni na ngani? Nigweba njani kanye
  37,155,Kanti aniqaphelisisi na
  37,156,Okanye mhlawumbi ninegunya elicacileyo nina
  37,157,Yizani nencwadi yenu kaloku ukuba ninenyaniso
  37,158,"Kananjalo baye baqamba ukuhlobana phakathi kwaKhe neeJinni, kodwa zona iiJinni ziyazi (kakuhle) okokuba ziza kuma (phambi kwaKhe ziphendule ngezenzo zazo)"
  37,159,"Uzuko\tlonke\tmalube\tkuAllâh!\t(Okude\tlee)\tkoko bakwayamanisa naYe"
  37,160,"Ngaphandle kwezicaka zika-Allâh, Awazikhethayo"
  37,161,Ngoko ke inene nina bahedeni ndawonye nabo nibanqulayo (izinyanya)
  37,162,Abangekhe balahlekise (nabani na kumakholwa) bamwexule kuYe (uAllâh)
  37,163,Ngaphandle kwalowo umiselwe ukuba atshe esiHogweni
  37,164,Yaye akukho namnye kuthi (ingelosi) koko unendawo yakhe eyaziwayo
  37,165,Kananjalo thina (zingelosi) sima ngokwemigca (sithandaze phambi koAllah)
  37,166,Yaye futhi thina (zingelosi) inene singabo bazukisa uAllâh
  37,167,Kananjalo bona (abahedeni) babedla ngokuthi
  37,168,“Ukuba sasibe naye umlumkisi njengabantu bamandulo
  37,169,Sasiya kuba zizicaka zika-Allâh ezikhethiweyo
  37,170,Kodwa (ngoku i’Kur’ân ifikile) abakholwa kuyo. Ngoko ke baza kwazi
  37,171,"Inene lona ilizwi leThu sele liphumile, kwamandulo mayela neziCaka zeThu abaProfeti"
  37,172,Elokuba ngabo ngokwenene abaza kuba noloyiso
  37,173,Kwanokuba imikhosi yeThu yiyo eza kuba yeyoyisayo
  37,174,Shenxa ke kubo (wena Muhammad) okwethutyana
  37,175,Ubajonge yaye baza kusibona (isohlwayo)
  37,176,Ingaba bafuna ukuba isohlwayo sikhawuleziswe
  37,177,"Ke kaloku ukuhla kwaso singena emizini yabo, iya kuba mbi intsasa (yaloo mini) kwabo babelunyukisiwe"
  37,178,Ngoko ke (wena Muhammad) bashiye okwethutyana
  37,179,"Ubajonge, yaye baza kubona (isohlwayo)"
  37,180,"Uzuko lonke malube seNkosini yakho, iNkosi yobunganga namandla (Ekude lee) koko bakwayamanisa naYo"
  37,181,Uxolo malube kubaThunywa
  37,182,"Neendumiso zonke mazibe kuAllâh, iNkosi uMlondolozi wamazwe"
  38,1,Sâd. Nge’Kur’ân enenkumbuzo
  38,2,Nakanye abo bangakholwayo basekuphikiseni okuyinkukhumalo yobuxoki
  38,3,Zingaphi izizukulwana eSazitshabalalisayo ngaphambili kunabo! Ke kaloku zakhala kwaba kungasekho xesha lakubaleka
  38,4,"Kananjalo (ama-Arabhu angakholwayo) amangalisekile kukuba kufike uMlumkisi kuwo ephuma phakathi kwawo. Yaye abangakholwayo bathi: “Lo (Mprofeti uMuhammad) ngumenzi wemilingo, ixoki"
  38,5,"Ingaba udibanise oothixo bonke baba nguthixo omnye? Inene, yinto engummangaliso le"
  38,6,"Ke kaloku abaziinkokeli phakathi kwabo bahamba besithi: “Nina hlalani nibambelele koothixo benu! Inene le yinto equlunqwe (ngokuchasene nani)"
  38,7,"Asizanga siyive into (enjengale) kwinkolo yale mihla (ubuKhristu), asintoyimbilengaphandlekokubangumqambo"
  38,8,"Ingaba iNkumbuzo1 ityhilwe kuye (yedwa) phakathi kwethu?” Unotshe, eneneni bona basezintandabuzweni ngeNkumbuzo yaM! Nakanye, abakasingcamli isohlwayo (saM)"
  38,9,"Makube mhlawumbi banoovimba benceba yeNkosi yakho, uSomandla, uMboneleli wokwenene"
  38,10,Okanye mhlawumbi ulongamelo lwamazulu nomhlaba nako konke okuphakathi kuwo lolwabo? Ukuba kunjalo ke mabanyuke kaloku (beze emazulwini) ngeendlela (zabo)
  38,11,Baya kuba ngumkhosi owoyisiweyo njengemikhosi yobumbano yamandulo (eyoyiswayo)
  38,12,Phambi kwabo (baninzi) abaphikisa (abathunywa) abantu bakwaNûh nabakwa’Ad; nabakwaFir’awn umfo wezibonda (awayesohlwaya ngazo abantu)
  38,13,NabakwaThamûd nabantu bakwaLût nabemi baseziNkunini abo ke yayingabantu bobumbano
  38,14,Akukho namnye kubo ongazanga abaphike abaThunywa. Ngoko ke isohlwayo saM sathetheleleka
  38,15,Aba ke balindele isithonga esinye kuphela seXilongo akuyi kubakho kuthotha nasiphelo kuso
  38,16,"Bathi: “Nkosi yethu! Khawulezisa (Usinike iiNcwadi zezenzo zethu ezilungileyo nezigwenxa ukuze sizibone) ingekafiki iMini yamatyala"
  38,17,"Yibanomondewena(Muhammad) mayelanokobakuthethayo, ukhumbule kananjalo isiCaka seThu uDâwûd wanyamezela ngamandla. Inene yena wayehlala ebuyela (kuThi) ngezinto zonke (awayezenza), enenguquko"
  38,18,Senza iintaba ukuba zizukise iindumiso zeThu kunye naye (uDâwûd) emva kwemini nasekuphumeni kwelanga kude kube semini emaqanda
  38,19,"Zenza njalo neentaka zahlangana, zamthobela zonke (uDâwûd)"
  38,20,Senza ubukumkani bakhe baba namandla Samnika ubulumko nokugweba ngokulungileyo ngentetho nangokuthabatha isigqibo
  38,21,Ingaba iindaba zababangisani ababini zifikile na kuwe? Xa batsiba udonga lwendawo yakhe yokuthandazela
  38,22,"Bathi bakungena kuye uDâwûd wothuka. Bathi bona: “Musa ukoyika, (thina singabantu ababangisanayo) ababini, omnye kuthi wone omnye, ngoko ke gweba phakathi kwethu ngenyaniso. Ungasiphathi ngentswela bulungisa, usikhokelele kananjalo eNdleleni elungileyo.”"
  38,23,"(Omnye kubo wathi): “Umzalwana wam lo unezimvu ezingamashumi asithoba anethoba, ndibe mna ndinenye kuphela kodwa (ngoko kunjalo) uthi: ‘Ndinike yona.’ Kwaye uyandongamela ngokuthetha.”"
  38,24,"UDâwûd (engalibazisanga) wathi: “Ukonile ngokufuna imvu yakho ukuba ayongeze kwezakhe. Kambe maninzi amahlulelane acinezelanayo, ngaphandle kwabo bakholwayo, benze izenzo ezilungileyo yaye bambalwa.” Ke kaloku uDâwûd waqikelela okokuba beSimvavanya wacela itarhu eNkosini yakhe, wawa phantsi waqubuda wabuyela kuAllâh ngenguquko"
  38,25,"Samxolela ke ngoko, ukanti okwakhe kukuba kufuphi naThi nendawo yokubuyela (iPaladesi)"
  38,26,"Hini na Dâwûd! Inene wena Sikubekele ukuba ube ngummeli ehlabathini; ngoko ke gweba ngokusenyanisweni, ungalandeli iminqweno yakho ngokuba iya kukuphambukisa eNdleleni ka-Allâh Inene abo baphambukayo eNdleleni ka-Allâh baya kufumana isohlwayo esibuhlungu ngokuba bona baye balibala ngeMini yemibuzo"
  38,27,Kanti ke Asidalanga amazulu nomhlaba nako konke okukuwo ngaphandle kwenjongo! Leyo yingcinga yabo bangakholwayo! Yeha ke kwabo bangakholwayo eMlilweni
  38,28,"Ingaba Siza kuphatha abo bakholwayo, benza izenzo ezilungileyo njengabenzi bobubi emhlabeni okanye Siphathe abo bahlonela uAllâh njengezingcoli"
  38,29,"(Le) yiNcwadi (i’Kur’ân) eSiyithumele kuwe, izele ziintsikelelo, khon’ukuze bacamngcisise ngeeVesi zayo aze namadoda anengqiqo phakathi kwabo akhumbule"
  38,30,Kananjalo uDâwûd Sampha uSulaymân. Esinjani ukulunga sona isiCaka! Inene yena wayehlala ebuyela (kuThi) ngenguquko
  38,31,Kwathi emva kwemini kwakwenziwa umboniso phambi kwakhe wamahashe aqeqeshiweyo omkhosi wokulwa imfazwe
  38,32,"Wathi yena: “Mna ndiye ndathanda (la mahashe) endaweni yokukhumbula iNkosi yam, lada ixesha (lomthandazo wasemva kwemini) laphela, (nelanga) lafihlakala kwisigqubuthelo (sobusuku).”"
  38,33,"Waza wathi: “Waziseni kum wahambahambisa isandla sakhe emilenzeni yawo nasezintanyeni zawo kwada kwaya kuphela umboniso"
  38,34,"Kananjalo Savavanya uSulaymân, Sabeka umzimba (ongenabomi) waza wabuyela (kuAllâh ngenguquko nangentobeko)"
  38,35,"Wathi: “Nkosi yam ndixolele, Undiphe ubukumkani obungasokuze bube bobakhe nabani na emva kwam: inene Wena unguSokupha.”"
  38,36,"Ke kaloku Samenzela ukuba umoya umthobele, wawuvuthuza ngocoselelo, ngokomyalelo wakhe, naphi na apho athanda khona"
  38,37,Kanti namashayâtini (ooSathana) nabo bonke abakhi neendadi
  38,38,Nabanye ababebotshwe ngamakhamandela
  38,39,"(UAllâh Wathi kuSulayman): “Esi sisipho seThu ngoko ke sisebenzise okanye usigcine kuwe, akukho nto iza kubuzwa (kuwe) ngaso.”"
  38,40,"Inene okwakhe kukuba secaleni kweThu, nokubuyela kokulungileyo ePaladesi"
  38,41,"Khumbula kananjalo isicaka seThu uAyyûb ukucela kwakhe eNkosini yakhe (esithi): “Inene uShaytân undifumene ngenkxwaleko nangentuthumbo"
  38,42,"UAllâh Wathi: “Ngqisha emhlabeni ngonyawo lwakho: nanku umthombo wamanzi wokuba uhlambe kuwo, akwasisiselo esipholileyo"
  38,43,"Kananjalo Saphinda Sambuyisela usapho lwakhe, ndawonye nokunye okufana noko njengenceba evela kuThi, nenkumbuzo kwabo baqiqayo"
  38,44,"Uthathe ngesandla sakho isicithi sengca ubethe ngaso (umfazi wakho), ungasaphuli isithembiso sakho. Inene Thina Samfumana (uAyyûb) enomonde, esinjani ukulunga sona isicaka! Inene yena wayesoloko ebuyela (kuThi) ngenguquko"
  38,45,"Khumbula kananjalo isicaka seThu uIbrâhîm, uIs-hâ’k, noYa’kûb (bonke) abo babe namandla (okuSikhonza) nengqiqo (elungileyo) yenkolo"
  38,46,Inene Sabakhetha bona ngokubanika inkumbuzo yekhaya (lasemva kokufa)
  38,47,"Kananjalo bona bakunye naThi, yaye bangabakhethiweyo, abona balungileyo"
  38,48,"Khumbula uIsmâ’îl, uAlyasa’2 noDthul-kifil3, bonke (abo) ngabanye babo balungileyo"
  38,49,Le yinkumbuzo. Yaye inene okwabanyulu iya kuba kukubuyela okulungilelyo kwasePaladesi
  38,50,"E’Adn (eEden), uMyezo omasango awo aya kuvulelwa bona"
  38,51,Phakathi apho baya kungqiyama; apho baya kubiza indyebo yeziqhamo neziselo
  38,52,"Ukanti ecaleni kwabo iya kuba ngabafazi abanyulu abaya kuba bebambe amehlo abo (ukuba anganqweneli bambi ngaphandle kwabayeni babo), benobudala obulinganayo"
  38,53,Oku ke kuko oko nina bamoyikayo uAllâh nithenjiswa ngako ngeMini yamatyala
  38,54,(Kuya kuthiwa kubo)! “Inene le yimbonelelo yeThu kuni engasokuze iphele
  38,55,Oku kunjalo! Ke kaloku kubagabadeli iya kuba kukubuyela okubi (kwaseMlilweni)
  38,56,"EsiHogweni kulapho baza kutsha khona, hayi ukuba mbi kwaloo ndawo yokuphumla (kwabo)"
  38,57,Oku kunjalo! Mabangcamle (isohlwayo) ke ulwelo olubandayo nobubomvu (obuphuma ezilondeni)
  38,58,Nezinye (izohlwayo) ezikwanjalo zidityaniswe zonke
  38,59,Eli liqela Eliza lingxamile kuwe! Akuyi kubakho kwamkeleka kubo Inene bona baza kutsha eMlilweni
  38,60,"(Ababengabalandeli baya kukhala kwabo babalahlekisayo bathi): “Oku kwenu! Akukho kwamkeleka kuni! Nini aba basihlisela oku phezu kwethu (emhlabeni), hayi ububi bale ndawo yokuhlala.!”"
  38,61,"Baya kuthi: “Nkosi yethu! Nabani na owasihlisela oku, mongezele isohlwayo ngokuphindwe kabini eMlilweni!”"
  38,62,"Ke kaloku baya kuthi: “Kwenzeka ntoni na kanye kuthi ukuba singababoni abantu esasidla ngokubabala nabangalunganga"
  38,63,"Ingaba sasibenza izinto zokugculela, okanye mhlawumbi ngamehlo ethu asilelayo ukubabona?”"
  38,64,Inene leyo yinyaniso yokwenene baya kuphikisana abantu boMlilo
  38,65,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Mna ndinguMlumkisi kuphela yaye akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle koAllâh, Omnye, Ongenakuphikiswa"
  38,66,"INkosi yamazulu nomhlaba nako konke okuphakathi kwawo, uSomandla, uMxoleli.”"
  38,67,"Yithi: “Le ‘Kur’ân iziindaba ezinkulu"
  38,68,Ezo nina nizitshikilelayo
  38,69,"Mna andinalwazi lwaziphathazithunywa, xa zazipikisana, zixoxa (ngokudalwa komntu)"
  38,70,"Okutyhiliweyo\tkum\tkuphela\tkoku:\tkukuba\tmna ndinguMlumkisi ocacileyo.”"
  38,71,"Yabona! INkosi yakho yathi kwiingelosi: “Ndiza kudala umntu ngodongwe"
  38,72,"Ekumbumbeni kwaM, Ndamphefumlela umoya wakhe, niya kuwa niqubude kuye ke nina.”"
  38,73,Zaqubuda iingelosi zonke
  38,74,"Ngaphandle koIblîs (uSathana): waba nekratshi waza waba ngomnye wabangakholwayo"
  38,75,"UAllâh Wathi: “Hini na Iblîs! Yintoni na ekuthintelayo ukuba ungaqubudi kulowo Ndimdalileyo ngeZandla zaM zoziBini? Uzingca kakhulu na okanye ungoyena wabaphakamileyo abakhulu kusini na?”"
  38,76,"(UIblîs) wathi: “Mna ndingcono kunaye. Mna Undidale ngomlilo, yena Wamdala ngodongwe.”"
  38,77,"(UAllâh) Wathi: “Phuma umke apha; kuba wena ulahliwe"
  38,78,Yaye inene isiqalekiso saM siya kuba phezu kwakho kude kube yiMini yoMgwebo”
  38,79,"(UIblîs) wathi: “Nkosi yam! Ndimele kude kube yiMini yoVuko lwabafileyo.”"
  38,80,"(UAllâh) Wathi: “Inene wena ungomnye wabo bamelweyo"
  38,81,Kude kube lixesha elimisiweyo.”
  38,82,"(UIblîs)\twathi:\t“Ngamandla\taKho,\tinene\tmna\tndiya kubalahlekisa bonke"
  38,83,Ngaphandle kwezicaka zaKho ezikhethekileyo phakathi kwabo.”
  38,84,"(UAllâh) Wathi: “Yinyaniso (leyo) yaye inyaniso Ndithi (kuwe)"
  38,85,Ndiya kuzalisa isiHogo ngawe ndawonye nabo (bantu) balandela wena.”
  38,86,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Akukho ntlawuliso ndinibiza yona ngale (‘Kur’ân), ndingenguye nomnye wabaqambi (bobuxoki)"
  38,87,Yona le (‘Kur’ân) yinkumbuzo yendalo yonke
  38,88,Ke kaloku niza kuyazi inyaniso emveni kwethuba.”
  39,1,"IsiTyhilelo sale Ncwadi (i’Kur’ân) sivela kuAllâh, uSomandla, uSobulumko"
  39,2,"Sithumele i’Kur’ân kuwe (Muhammad) ngenyaniso: ngoko ke wena nqula uAllâh, wenze izenzo zenkolo ngokunyanisekileyo ngenxa ka-Allâh"
  39,3,"Inene inkolo yeka-Allâh kuphela. Abo bazithabathela bancedi bambi ngaphandle kwaKhe (besithi): “Sibanqulela ukuba basisondeze kuAllâh kuphela.’’ Inene uAllâh Uza kugweba phakathi kwabo mayela noko baphikisana ngako. Inene Akamkhokeli lowo ulixoki nongumchasikholo"
  39,4,"UkubauAllâhWayethandileukubanonyana,ngeWayemkhethe kwabo Wabadalayo kodwa Makazukiswe Yena. NguAllâh, Mnye, Yena akanakuphikiswa"
  39,5,"Yena Wadala amazulu nomhlaba ngenyaniso. Wenza ubusuku bumke emini ize nemini imke ebusuku kananjalo Wenza ilanga nenyanga ukuba nganye kuzo ibaleke ixesha elibekelweyo. Inene Yena nguSomandla, nguMxoleli"
  39,6,"Wanidala (nonke) ngesiqu (somntu) omnye (uAdam); Waza ngaye (lowo) Wenza umfazi wakhe, kananjalo Yena Unithobele izibini ezisibhozo (zezilwanyana zemfuyo). Yena Unidale ezibelekweni zoomama benu (Wenza) indalo emva kwendalo kwizigqubuthelo ezithathu zobumnyama. Lowo ke nguAllâh: iNkosi yakho. BobaKhe ubukumkani, akukho Thixo ngaphandle kwaKhe yintoni na eniphambhukisileyo"
  39,7,"Ukuba niye anakholwa, inene Yena uAllâh akukho nto Anifuna yona, Akakuthandi ukungakholwa ezicakeni zaKhe. Kananjalo ukuba niyabulela, Uyakuthanda oko kuni. Akukho mthwali wamithwalo uza kuthwaliswa umthwalo womnye. Ukanti eNkosini yenu kulapho niza kubuyela khona. Yaye Iza kunixelela ngezinto enazenzayo. Inene Yena nguMazi woko kusezifubeni (zabantu)"
  39,8,"Kanti ke xa umntu echukunyiswa bubuhlungu, uye athandaze eNkosini yakhe, abuyele kuYo ngenguquko: Kodwa Esakumbonelela ngezibele zaKhe, alibale ngoko ebekuthandazele ngaphambili, aze abe nabaphikisi baka Allâh khona ukuze baphambukise abanye abantu eNdleleni yaKhe. Yithi: “Kuvuyeleni ukungakholwa kwenu okwethutyana: inene nina ningabanye babo bangabahlali baseMlilweni!”"
  39,9,"Ingaba lowo uthobela uAllâh, uqubudayo okanye eme ngeenyawo (athandaze) ngeeyure zobusuku, esoyika uBomi oBuzayo, enethembalencebayeNkosiyakhe,(uyafananalowo ungakholwayo na)? Yithi: “Ingaba abo baziyo bayafana nabo bangaziyo?” Inene ngabantu bengqiqo kuphela abaya kukhumbula (bathabathe isifundo kwiiVesi ze’Kur’ân)"
  39,10,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Hini na zicaka zam ezikholwayo! Yoyikani iNkosi yenu, nenze amaxanduva wenu kuYo, mhle (umvuzo) wabo benza okulungileyo kweli hlabathi, ukanti umhlaba ka-Allâh uphangalele1. Ngabo banomonde kuphela abaza kufumana umvuzo wabo ngokugcweleyo ngaphandle kokumiswa ematyaleni"
  39,11,"Yithi: “Inene mna ndiyalelwe ukuba ndinqule uAllâh Yedwa ngokuthi ndiMthobele, ndenze izenzo zenkolo ngenxa yaKhe kuphela"
  39,12,Kananjalo mna ndiyalelwe (oku) khon’ukuze ndibe ngowokuqala kwabo (bazinikelayo kuAllâh) bangama Muslim.”
  39,13,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Inene ukuba ndingangayithobeli iNkosi yam, ndoyika isohlwayo seMinikazi eNkulu"
  39,14,"Yithi: “NguAllâh Yedwa endimnqula ngokwenza izenzo zenkolo ngokunyanisekileyo ngenxa yaKhe kuphela"
  39,15,"Ke ngoko khonzani loo nto nithande ukuyikhonza ngaphandle kwaKhe Yithi (Muhammad): “Abalahlekelwa (bokwenene) ngabo baza kulahlekelwa ziziqu zabo neentsapho zabo ngoMhla woVuko. Inene leyo iya kuba yilahleko ecacileyo.’’"
  39,16,"Baya kuba nezigqumathelo zoMlilo phezu kwabo nezigqumathelo zoMlilo nangaphantsi kwabo Ngako oku uAllâh Woyikisa izicaka zaKhe: “Hini na zicaka zaM, yoyikani Mna ke ngoko.’’"
  39,17,"Abo bazikhwebulayo kwizinto ezingcolileyo bangazikhonzi baze babuyele kuAllâh okwabo ziindaba ezivuyisayo, ngoko ke vakalisa iindaba ezilungileyo kwizicaka zaM"
  39,18,"Ke bona abo baliphulaphulayo ilizwi, balandele okulungileyo kulo. Abo ngabo uAllâh Abakhokeleyo yaye abo ngabantu bengqiqo"
  39,19,Ingaba lowo ummiselo wesohlwayo umfaneleyo (uyafana nalowo uzikhwebulayo ekungcoleni? Ingaba wena Muhammad uza kukwazi ukumhlangula lowo useMlilweni)
  39,20,"Kodwa abo bayoyikayo iNkosi yabo (uAllâh) benze imisebenzi yeemfanelo zabo kuYe, okwabo ngamagumbi aphakamileyo abawakhelwayo, elinye phezu kwelinye, ekumpompoza imilambo phantsi kwawo: Esi sisithembiso sika-Allâh; yaye uAllâh Akasileli kwisithembiso (saKhe)"
  39,21,"Akuboni na ukuba uAllâh Uthumela amanzi (emvula) esuka esibhakabhakeni, Awenze angene emhlabeni, eyimithombo? Aze emva koko Enze kuhlume iimveliso eziyimibala ngemibala zize emva koko zitshazwe (zibune), nizibone zijika ziba mthubi, Aze Azenze zome zibe zizijungqu ezaphukileyo? Inene kuko oku kukho inkumbuzo kubantu bengqiqo"
  39,22,Ingaba lowo usifuba sakhe uAllâh Asenze savuleka kwi-Islam khona ukuze abe sekukhanyeni kweNkosi yakhe (uyafana nalowo ungeloMuslim). Yeha ke kwabo bantliziyo zabo zilukhuni ekukhumbuleni uAllâh! Bona basekulahlekeni okucacileyo
  39,23,"UAllâh Uthumele eyona ntetho ilungileyo, iNcwadi (i’Kur’ân), enezahluko ezifanayo neziphinda-phindiweyo. Izikhumba zabo bayoyikayo iNkosi yabo ziyangcangcazela ngayo. Ke kaloku izikhumba zabo neentliziyo zabo zithambela inkumbulo ka-Allâh. Yena Ukhokela lowo Athande ukumkhokela ngayo. Ke lowo ulahlekiswe nguAllâh akayi kuba namkhokeli"
  39,24,"Ingaba lowo uza kugagana ngobuso bakhe nesohlwayo esoyikekayo ngoMhla woVuko (uyafana na nalowo uza kungena eMyezweni)? Kananjalo kuya kuthiwa kubenzi bobubi: “Ngcamlani enakwenzayo.’’"
  39,25,"Baphika abangaphambili kubo, saza isohlwayo seza kubo sivela kumacala ababengawacingelanga"
  39,26,Ngoko ke uAllâh Wabenza bangcamla ihlazo kobu bomi kodwa esikhulu sisohlwayo soBomi oBuzayo ukuba bebesazi
  39,27,Ke kaloku Sinike umntu kule ‘Kur’ân zonke iintlobo zemizekeliso khon’ukuze bakhumbule
  39,28,"I’Kur’ân yesiArabhu, engenabugoso-goso (kuyo) khon’ukuze baphephe ukungcola uAllâh Abayalele ukuba bakuphephe, baMoyike, benze amaxanduva abo kuYe"
  39,29,"uAllâh Wenza umzekeliso: indoda (esisicaka) yabantu abangamahlulelane amaninzi, axambulisanayo nendoda esisicaka senkosi enye kuphela: ingaba (ezi zicaka) zibini ziyafana xa zithelekiswa? Iindumiso mazibe kuAllâh! Kodwa uninzi lwabo alwazi"
  39,30,"Inene wena (Muhammad) uza kufa, kanti nabo baza kufa"
  39,31,Ke kaloku ngoMhla woVuko niya kuphikisana phambi kweNkosi yenu
  39,32,"Ngubani na owenza obona bugwenxa bukhulu kunalowo uthetha ubuxoki ngoAllâh, aphike inyaniso isakuba ifikile kuye! Alikho siHogweni na ikhaya labangakholwayo"
  39,33,Kananjalo yena (uMuhammad) uze nenyaniso yaye abo bakholwayo kuyo ngabanyulu
  39,34,"Baya kukufumana konke abakufunayo eNkosini yabo, lowo ngumvuzo wabenzi bokulungileyo"
  39,35,"Khon’ukuze uAllâh Abahlawulele ngokungcola abakwenzayo, Abanike umvuzo olingana noko (kulungileyo) bazama kangangoko ukukwenza"
  39,36,"Akanelanga na uAllâh kwisicaka saKhe? Kodwa basazama ukunoyikisa ngabo babanqulayo ngaphandle kwaKhe! Lowo ulahlekiswe nguAllâh, akuyi kubakho mkhokeli kuye"
  39,37,Nabani na lowo uAllâh amkhokeleyo akuyi kubakho mlahlekisi. AyingoAllâh na uMnini mpindezelo
  39,38,"Ukanti ke xa unokubabuza: “Ngubani owadala amazulu nomhlaba? ‘’Ngokuqinisekileyo baza kuthi: nguAllâh (Owadalileyo)’’ Yithi wena: “Ndixeleleni ke ezi zinto nizinqulayo ngaphandle koAllâh ukuba uAllâh Angagqiba ekubeni Andenze ububi zingabususa zona ububi baKhe? Okanye ukuba (uAllâh) Angandenzela inceba yaKhe zingayithintela inceba yaKhe?’’ Yithi Wanele kum uAllâh; mababeke ithemba labo kuYe bonke abo bakholwayo"
  39,39,"Yithi: “Hini na bantu bakuthi! Yenzani ngendlela yenu Mna ndenze (ngendlela yam). Yaye niza kwazi"
  39,40,Lowo uza kufikelwa sisohlwayo esilihlazo ngulowo uza kuhlelwa sisohlwayo sanaphakade
  39,41,"Sityhilele uluntu iNcwadi kuwe ngenyaniso, ngoko ke lowo wamkela isiKhokelo, usamkelela isiqu sakhe nalowo uphambukayo, uziphambukisela ilahleko yakhe, wena ke (Muhammad) awungomlondolozi wabo"
  39,42,"NguAllâh Othabatha imiphefumlo yabo ngexesha lokufa kwabo, nabo bafa bengalelanga. Abo Amisele ukuba bafe, Uyababamba (bangabuyeli ebomini), kodwa bonke abanye Ubathumela (emizimbeni yabo) ixesha elimisiweyo inene kuyo le nto kukho imiqondiso kwabo bacamngcayo"
  39,43,"Bazithabathele (thixo bambi) ukuba babe ngabathetheleli ngaphandle koAllâh kusini na? Yithi: “Nangona bengenamandla naphezu kwayiphi na into, bengenayo nengqondo?’’"
  39,44,"Yithi: “Intethelelo yonke yeka-Allâh. BobaKhe ubukumkani bamazulu nomhlaba ukanti kukuYe apho niza kubuyiselwa khona.’’"
  39,45,"Xa uAllâh Ekhankanywa Yedwa, iintliziyo zabo bangakholwayo kuBomi Obuzayo zizala kukucaphuka kodwa xa (ezinye izithixo) zikhankanywa ngaphandle kwaKhe, yabona, baba nochulumanco"
  39,46,"Yithi: “O Allâh! Mdali wamazulu nomhlaba! (Wena) Mazi wokungabonwayo nokubonwayo! Uza kugweba phakathi kwezicaka zaKho ngoko zaziphikisana ngako.’’"
  39,47,"Abo benza ubugwenxa, ukuba bebenokuba nako konke okusemhlabeni, nangaphezulukunako, bebezakunikelangako njengentlawulo (yokuzikhulula) kwintlungu yesohlwayo ngeMini yoMgwebo: kodwa kukho into eza kugagana nabo evela kuAllâh, abebengayazi"
  39,48,"Ke kaloku ukungcola kwezenzo zabo baza kukubona, yaye baza kurhangqelwa ngokupheleleyo koko babekugculela"
  39,49,"Xa ububi bumchukumisa umntu, uthandaza kuThi (acele uncedo): (Sithi sisakumhlangula kobo bubi) sibujike bube luBabalo oluvela kuThi, (asuke) athi yena : “Kube ngenxa yolwazi lwam kuphela ukuze ndifumane oku,” Nakanye (olu) luvavanyo kuphela, kodwa uninzi lwabo alwazi"
  39,50,"Abo bangaphambili kunabo batsho njalo, kodwa (konke) oko babe nako akuzanga kubancede nto"
  39,51,"Ngoko ke iziphumo ezingcolileyo zoko bakwenzayo zabafumana, abenzi bobubi (besi sizukulwana) iziphumo ezingcolileyo zezenzo zabo ziza kubafumana (nabo), yaye abayi kuze bakwazi ukuphuncula"
  39,52,"AbazinaukubauAllâh WandiselalowoAthandeukumandisela imbonelelo, Ancitshe (lowo Athande ukumncitsha) Inene kuko oku kukho imiqondiso kubantu abakholwayo"
  39,53,"Yithi: Hini na zicaka zaM ezigabadeleyo ngokuchasene neziqu zazo! Musani ukulahla ithemba ngenceba ka-Allâh: kuba uAllâh Uxolela zonke izono: ngokuba Yena nguMxoleli, nguSozinceba"
  39,54,"Kananjalo buyelani (kuAllâh) ngenguquko nangentobeko ngokholo lokwenene eNkosini yenu, nizithobe kuYo singekanifikeli isohlwayo, emva koko aniyi kuba sancedwa"
  39,55,"Yaye landelani okona kulungileyo koko kuthunyelwe kuni kuvela eNkosini yenu, singekehli isohlwayo phezu kwenu ngequbuliso ningaqondanga"
  39,56,"Kuba hleze umntu athi: “Kowu madoda, ndibuhlungu ngokungabi nahoyo ngoAllâh yaye ndasuka mna ndaba ngomnye wabo bagculelayo!’’"
  39,57,"Okanye: athi “Ukuba uAllâh Wayendikhokele, ndandiya kuba ngomnye wamalungisa!’’"
  39,58,"Okanye athi xa ngoko sele esibona isohlwayo: “Akwaba bendinokuphinda ndinikwe elinye ithuba inene bendiya kuba ngomnye wabenzi bokulungileyo!’’"
  39,59,"(Impendulo iya kuba kuthiwe kuye): “Nakanye, iiVesi zaM zazifikile kuwe, kodwa wena wazala; waba nenkukhumalo, wangomnye wabo bangakholwayo.”"
  39,60,Kananjalo ngomhla woVuko uza kubabona abo baxokayo ngoAllâh ubuso babo buya kuba mnyama. Alikho siHogweni na kanene ikhaya labakhukhumeleyo
  39,61,"Ke kaloku uAllâh Uya kubasindisa abo banyulu, Abangenise ezindaweni zabo zempumelelo. Ukungcola akuyi kubachukumisa, bengayi kuxhalaba"
  39,62,"UAllâh nguMdali wezinto zonke, yaye nguMlondolozi wezinto zonke"
  39,63,"ZezaKhe izitshixo zamazulu nomhlaba. Ke kaloku abo bangakholwayo kwiiVesi zika-Allâh, ngabo kanye abaya kuba ngabalahlekelwa"
  39,64,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Nina niyalela mna ukuba ndikhonze (thixo bambi) ngaphandle koAllâh kusini na ziyathandini !’’"
  39,65,"Ukanti kuye kwatyhilwa kuwe (Muhammad) njengoko kwakunjalo kwabakwandulelayo (kwathiwa): “Ukuba nithe nayamanisa abanye kunqulo luka-Allâh inene izenzo zenu ziya kuba lilize yaye inene niya kuba ngabanye babalahlekelwa.”"
  39,66,"Ewe nje! Wena nqula uAllâh, ube kunye nabo banombulelo"
  39,67,"Abenzanga mlinganiselo wabulungisa ufanelekileyo ngoAllâh, Kanti ngoMhla woVuko umhlaba wonke uza kufunjathwa siSandla saKhe. Yaye amazulu wona aya kusongwa eSandleni saKhe sokunene. Uzuko malube kuYe, Ungentla kwazo zonke izinto abazayamanisa naYe"
  39,68,"Ke kaloku iXilongo liya kuvuthelwa, baze bonke abasemangcwabeni banyamalale, ngaphandle kwalowo uAllâh Athandileyo. Liya kuvuthelwa okwesibini, yabona, baya kuma bejongile (belindele okuza kwenzeka)"
  39,69,"Nomhlaba uya kubengezela kukukhanya kweNkosi yawo, ize iNcwadi ibekwe (ivuliwe), baze abaProfeti namangqina baziswe ngaphambili, kuze kugwetywe phakathi kwabo ngokusenyanisweni, yaye abayi kwenziwa bugwenxa"
  39,70,Ke kaloku umntu ngamnye uya kuhlawula ngokugcweleyo ngako akwenzileyo. Yaye (uAllâh) Ukwazi kakuhle abakwenzayo
  39,71,"Kananjalo bona abo bangakholwayo baya kuqhutyelwa esiHogweni bengamaqela, de bafike kuso, amasango aso aya kuvulwa, ke kaloku abagcini baso baya kuthi: “Azanga abaThunywa bafike kuni na bephuma kwakuni, benicengcelezela iiVesi zenkosi yenu (uAllâh), benilumkisa ngale ndibano yaleMini yenu na?’’ Baya kuthi bona: “Ewe,’’ Kodwa lona ilizwi lesohlwayo liya kuthetheleleka ngokuchasene nabangakholwayo"
  39,72,"Kuya kuthiwa (kubo): “Ngenani ke emasangweni esiHogo, nihlale apho. Inene, hayi ububi bekhaya lezikhukhumali"
  39,73,"Ke bona abo bawenzayo umsebenzi wabo (wonqulo) eNkosini yabo baya kukhokelelwa eMyezweni bengamaqela, de bafike kuwo, amasango awo aya kuvulwa, ke kaloku abagcini bawo baya kuthi: “Salâmun ‘alaykum (uxolo malube nani), nenze kakuhle, ngenani ke ngoko nihlale apho ngaphakathi.”"
  39,74,"Ke kaloku baya kuthi: “Iindumiso zonke nemibulelo mazibe kuAllâh, Ozalisekise isithembiso saKhe, Wasenza saba ziindlalifa zeli lizwe, singahlala ePaladesi naphi na apho sithande khona, onjani ukuba mhle wona umvuzo wabasebenzi (bokulungileyo)"
  39,75,"Kananjalo uya kuzibona iingelosi zingqonge iTrone (ka- Allâh) macala onke, zizukisa iindumiso zeNkosi yazo (uAllâh). Ke kaloku zonke (izidalwa) ziya kugwetywa ngenyaniso yaye kuya kuthiwa: “Iindumiso nemibulelo yonke mayibe kuAllâh, iNkosi uMlondolozi wanaphakade"
  40,1,"Hâ, Mîm"
  40,2,"IsiTyhileloseNcwadi(i’Kur’ân)sivelakuAllâh,uSobunganga, uSolwazi"
  40,3,"UMxoleli wezono, uMamkeli wenguquko, Owohlwaya kabuhlungu, UMnini ndyebo, akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaKhe, kukuYe apho kuza kubuyelwa khona"
  40,4,"Akukho bani uyiphikayo imiqondiso ka-Allâh ngaphandle kwabo bangakholwayo, ngoko ke wena ungakhohliswa yintshukumo yabo ezweni lonke"
  40,5,"Abantu bakwaNûh baphika ngaphambili kunabo nabangakholwayo emva kwabo, ukanti sizwe ngasinye saba nenjongo (yokwenza iyelenqe) ngokuchasene noMthunywa waso, ngenjongo yokumhlasela, kananjalo baphikisana (ngokusebenzisa) ubuxoki (bezama) ukutshitshisa inyaniso. Ndabahlasela ke, (sabasibi) kanjani ke isohlwayo saM"
  40,6,Lasebenza ngolo hlobo ke ilizwi leNkosi yakho kwabo bangakholwayo yaba kukuba bona baya kuba ngamadlelane oMlilo
  40,7,"Ezo (ngelosi) zithwala iTrone nezo ziyingqongileyo zizukisa (uAllâh) ngendumiso yeNkosi yazo yaye ziyakholwa kuYe zicelela noxolo abo bakholwayo, (zisithi): “Nkosi yethu Wena Ugubungele izinto zonke ngenceba yakho nolwazi, xolela abo baguqukileyo, balandela iNdlela yaKho, Ubakhusele kananjalo kwisohlwayo soMlilo wesiHogo"
  40,8,"Nkosi yethu bangenise eMiyezweni yokuhlala naphakade owabathembisa ngayo bona, nabani na owayengumenzi wobulungisa kooyise babo, kubalingane babo nakubantwana babo. Inene nguWe uSobunganga, uSobulumko"
  40,9,"Ubakhusele kananjalo kwiziphumo ezingcolileyo (zezenzo zabo). Ke kaloku lowo Umkhuselayo ekungcoleni kweziphumo zaloo Mini Uya kuba Umenzele inceba, yaye oko yiyona mpumelelo inkulu.”"
  40,10,"Inene abo bangakholwayo kuya kuthethwa kuthiwe kubo: “Inkcaso ka-Allâh kuni yayingaphezulu kunokuchasana kwenu ukanti nanimenyiwe kodwa nina anakholwa.’’"
  40,11,"Baya kuthi: “Nkosi yethu, Wasenza asabi nabomi kabini, Wasinika ubomi kabini, yaye siyazivuma izono zethu, ingaba ikhona na indlela yokuphuma?’’"
  40,12,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Oku kungenxa yokuba ngelixa uAllâh Wayethandazwa, (Enqulwa) Yedwa nina naye anakholwa, Kodwa kwathi kusakwayanyaniswa abanye kuYe nakholwa. (Ngoku) ke uMgwebo ngoka-Allâh Ophakamileyo, Omkhulu.’’"
  40,13,"NguYe Onibonisa imiqondiso yaKhe, Athumele kuni imbonelelo ivela esibhakabhakeni. Kodwa akukho namnye oya kukhumbula ngaphandle kwalowo ubuyelayo (aguquke)"
  40,14,"Ngokokewena,thandazakuAllâh,unyanisekekuYeenkolweni enokuba abangakholwayo bakuchase (kangakanani) na oko"
  40,15,"(Yena uAllâh) nguSobunganga, Ongentla kwayo (yonke) imimiselo, Umnini weTrone; Uphefumlela umyalelo waKhe kulowo Athandileyo kwizicaka zaKhe, ukuba alumkise ngeMini yendibano"
  40,16,"Mhla baziswa ngaphambili akukho nto emayela nabo iya kufihlakala kuAllâh. Lelikabani na lonke igunya naMhlanje? Lelika-Allâh, Omnye Ongaphikiswayo"
  40,17,"NaMhla umphefumlo ngamnye uya kuvuzwa ngoko wakusebenzelayo. Akuyi kubakho ntswela-bulungisa namhlanje! IneneuAllâh, Uyakhawulezaukufakaembuzweni"
  40,18,"Balumkise (Muhammad), ngeMini esondelayo, xa iintliziyo ziya kuba semqaleni, (zixhalabile). Ke kaloku kubenzi bobubi akuyi kubakho mhlobo usenyongweni kungayi kubakho mthetheleli uya kuthotyelwa"
  40,19,(UAllâh) Uyakwazi okukholisa amehlo (abo) noko kufihlwa zizifuba (zabo)
  40,20,"Kananjalo uAllâh Ugweba ngenyaniso, lo gama abo bathandaza kubo ngaphandle kwaKhe bengagwebi nganto. Inene uAllâh nguSokuva, uSokubona"
  40,21,"Abakhenkethanga na ehlabathini babone ukuba sabanjani na isiphelo sabo babandulelayo? Bona babebakhulu kunabo ngamandla nangenkangeleko elizweni, kodwa uAllâh Wabahlasela ngezono zabo. Abazanga babe namkhuseli kuAllâh"
  40,22,"Oko kwaba ngenxa yokuba abathunywa babo beza kubo nemiqondiso ecacileyo, kodwa abakholwa, Wabahlasela ke uAllâh. Inene Yena Unamandla, Wohlwaya kabuhlungu"
  40,23,Kananjalo Sathumela uMûsâ nemiqondiso yeThu negunya elicacileyo
  40,24,"KuFir’awn, uHâmân no’Kârûn, kodwa bona bathi: “Yena (uMûsâ) ngumenzi wemilingo nexoki.’’"
  40,25,"Ekufikeni kwakhe nenyaniso kubo evela kuThi, bathi bona: “Bulalani oonyana babo bakholwa kunye naye, nigcine abasetyhini babo bephila.” Kodwa icebo labangakholwayo alinto yanto ngaphandle kokuba kukulahleka"
  40,26,"Ke kaloku uFir’awn wathi: “Ndiyekeni ndimbulale uMûsâ yena abize eNkosini yakhe. Inene mna ndoyikisela ukuba uya kuyijika inkolo yenu kungenjalo enze ubutshinga1 emhlabeni.”"
  40,27,"Kodwa uMûsâ wathi yena: “Inene mna ndicela ukhuseleko ngeNkosiyam EkwayiNkosiyakhongokuchasenenayenabani na osisikhukhumali ongakholwayo kwiMini yamatyala.”"
  40,28,"Ke kaloku indoda ekholwayo yakuloFir’awn eyayilufihlile ukholo lwayo, yathi: “Ingaba uza kubulala indoda ngenxa yokusuka ithi: “INkosi yam nguAllâh”, lo gama ikunike imiqondiso ecacileyo evela eNkosini yakho? Ukanti ke ukuba iyaxoka, siya kuba phezu kwayo isiphumo sokuxoka kwayo, kodwa ukuba kuthe kanti ithetha inyaniso, kuya kukuthwaxa okuyinxalenye yoko ikuthembisa ngako. Inene uAllâh Akamkhokeli lowo ungumgabadeli nolixoki"
  40,29,"Hini na bantu bakuthi, ulawulo lolwenu namhlanje elizweni. Kodwa ke ngubani na oza kusikhusela kwisohlwayo sika- Allâh sakufika kuthi?” UFir’awn wathi: “Mna andinibonisi nto ngaphandle kwale ndiyibonayo, yaye andinikhokeleli ntweni ngaphandle (kokunikhokelela) kokulungileyo.’’"
  40,30,"Wathi kananjalo lowo wayekholwa (kuMûsâ): “Hini na bantu bakuthi, inene ndiyanoyikisela kokuza kunihlela okunjengoko kwehla ngemini yamadlelane"
  40,31,Njengesehlo sabantu bakwaNûh nabakwa’Ad nabakwaThamûd nabo basemveni kwabo. Kanti ke uAllâh Akanqweneli (kwenza) ntswela bulungisa kwizicaka zaKhe
  40,32,"Kananjalo hini na bantu bakuthi, inene mna ndiyanoyikisela kwiMini yokuBizwa"
  40,33,"Mini leyo niya kuphethuka nibaleke; akukho mkhuseli ninaye kuAllâh, yaye lowo uAllâh Amyekele ekulahlekeni akukho bani uya kumkhokela"
  40,34,"Kananjalo inene uYûsuf weza kuni, mandulo, enemiqondiso ecacileyo, kodwa nina anizanga nipheze ukukuthandabuza oko weza nako kuni: wada wafa, naqala nina nathi “Akukho Mprofeti uAllâh Aya kumthumela emveni kwakhe. Wenza njalo ke uAllâh ukukhokelela ekulahlekeni lowo ungumenzi wobubi nalowo uthandabuza izilumkiso zika-Allâh"
  40,35,"Abo baphikisanayo ngeeVesi zika-Allâh bengenamagunya afikileyo kubo, oko kulihlazo kwaye kuchaseke kakhulu kuAllâh nakwabo bakholwayo. Uyitywina kanjalo ke intliziyo yakhe wonke ubani osisikhukhumali, ongumcinezeli"
  40,36,"Ke kaloku uFir’awn wathi: “Hini na Hâmân! Ndakhele ibhotwe eliphakamileyo ukuze ndikwazi ukuba neendlela"
  40,37,"“Iindlela (zokufikelela) emazulwini, ndikwazi nokuba ndibone uThixo kaMûsâ: kodwa inene mna ndimcingela ukuba (uMûsâ) lixoki.” Kwenziwa kwabonakala kulungile emehlweni kaFir’awn ukungcola kwezenzo zakhe yaye waye wathintelwa ukuba angangeni eNdleleni elungileyo; kananjalo icebo likaFir’awn alizanga likhokelele ntweni ngaphandle kwelahleko nentshabalalo"
  40,38,"Ke kaloku yena lowo wakholwayo wathi: “Hini na bantu bakuthi landelani mna; ndiya kunikhokelela eNdleleni yezenzo ezilungileyo"
  40,39,"Hini na bantu bakuthi: ubomi beli hlabathi abunto yanto ngaphandle kokuba lulonwabo lwethutyana, ke bona obelizayo, inene, bona likhaya lokuhlala lanaphakade elo"
  40,40,"Nabani na lowo wenza isenzo sokungcola akayi kubuyekezwa nganto yimbi ngaphandle kokufana noko (kubi akwenzileyo) kodwa yena lowo wenza okulungileyo, enokuba ngoyindoda na okanye ngowasetyhini, abe elikholwa, abo baya kungeniswa eMyezweni, banikwe isixhaso (sabo) apho ngaphandle komlinganiselo"
  40,41,Kananjalo Hini na bantu bakuthi kwenzeka njani na ukuba ndithi ndinimemela elusindisweni nibe nina nindimemela eMlilweni
  40,42,"Nina nindimemela ekubeni ndingakholwa kuAllâh nasekubeni ndayamanise endingenalwazi ngako kuYe, Mna ke ndinimemela kuSobunganga, uMxoleli"
  40,43,Oko nina nindimemela kuko akunayo (impendulo) xa kucelwa (kuko) kweli hlabathi nakwelizayo; ukanti kukuAllâh apho ukubuyela kwethu kukhoyo yaye inene abagabadeli baya kuba ngamadlelane oMlilo
  40,44,"Kanti ke niya kukukhumbula endikutshoyo kuni, yaye ndibeka ithemba lam kuAllâh. Inene uAllâh nguMjongi wezicaka zaKhe"
  40,45,Ke kaloku uAllâh Wamkhusela kumayelenqe angcolileyo ababewaqulunqile baza abantu bakwaFir’awn bagutyungelwa ngesona sibi isohlwayo
  40,46,"UMlilo; bagagana nawo ekuseni nangokuhlwa3. Kanti ngoMhla iMini yoVuko ivela (kuya kuthiwa): “Phosani (phakathi eMlilweni) abantu bakwaFir’awn bangene kwesona sohlwayo sibuhlungu.”"
  40,47,"Yabona! Baya kuphikisana phakathi eMlilweni, ababebuthathaka baya kuthi kwabo babekhukhumele: “Inene thina sasingabalandeli benu, ingaba niza kusiphumza, nithabathe (esenu) isabelo soMlilo na?’’"
  40,48,"Abo babekhukhumele baya kuthi: “Inene, sisonke sikuwo nathi Inene uAllâh Ugwebile phakathi kwezicaka zaKhe.’’"
  40,49,"Abo baseMlilweni baya kuthi kubagcini besiHogo: Celani eNkosini yenu ukuba isinciphisele ngemini enye kwisohlwayo.’’"
  40,50,"Baya kuthi: “Akuzanga kufike baThunywa nemiqondiso ecacileyo na kuni? Baya kuthi bona: “Ewe.’’ Baya kuphendula, “Ziceleleni nina (ngokwenu) kodwa isicelo sabangakholwayo asinto yanto ngaphandle kokuba kukulahleka”"
  40,51,Inene Thina Siya kubenza babe noloyiso abaThunywa bethu nabo bakholwayo ngoku besesemhlabeni kanti nangeMini amangqina aya kumiswa
  40,52,"NgeMini ukuzithethelela kwabo kungayi kubanceda abenzi bobugwenxa, yaye baya kuba nesiqalekiso, nelona khaya lakha lalibi (esiHogweni)"
  40,53,Kananjalo Thina Sanika uMûsâ isiKhokelo Senza aBantwana bakwaSirayeli baba ziindlalifa zesiBhalo
  40,54,Ukuba sibe sisiKhokelo nesikhumbuzi kwabo bangabokuqiqa
  40,55,"Ngoko ke wena (Muhammad) yiba nomonde, inene isithembiso sika-Allâh siyinyaniso, ucele itarhu lesono4 sakho, uzukise (uAllâh) ngendumiso yeNkosi ngokuhlwa nasekuseni"
  40,56,"Inene abo baphikisanayo ngokuphathelene nemiqondiso ka- Allâh bengenagunya lifikileyo kubo – akukho nto ezifubeni zabo ngaphandle kwenkukhumalo (bona ubuProfeti) asokuze babufumane. Ke wena funa ukhuseleko ngoAllâh, inene yena nguYe OnguSokuva, uSokubona"
  40,57,"Ukudalwa kwamazulu nomhlaba kukhulu ngenene kunokudalwa kwabantu: kodwa uninzi lwabantu alwazi"
  40,58,"Kanti abalingani abaziimfama nababonayo, (bengalingani kananjalo) abo bakholwayo, benza ubulungisa nabo benza ukungcola, kuncinane enikuqaphelayo"
  40,59,"Inene iYure iyeza yona, akukho ntandabuzo ngayo, kodwa abantu abaninzi abakholwa"
  40,60,"Ke kaloku iNkosi yakho Ithi: “Cela kuM; Ndiya kukuphendula Mna. Inene abo bakucekisayo ukunqulwa kwaM baya kungena esiHogweni bedelekile.”"
  40,61,NguAllâh Owanenzela ubusuku ukuze niphumle ngabo nemini (ukuba) ininike ukubona. Inene uAllâh nguMnini- Bubele eluntwini. Kodwa uninzi lwabantu alunambulelo
  40,62,"NguAllâh ke loWo, iNkosi yakho, uMdali wezinto zonke; akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaKhe, kanti nimfamekiseke njani na"
  40,63,"(Nabangaphambili) kunani baya bamfamekiseka ngolo hlobo, besala iiVesi zika-Allâh"
  40,64,"NguAllâh Onenzele umhlaba waba yindawo yokuzinza nesibhakabhaka saba luphahla, Wanibumba, Wanifezekisela izimo zenu Wanibonelela ngezinto ezilungileyo. NguAllâh ke loWo, iNkosi yenu; Usikelelekile uAllâh iNkosi, uMlondolozi wamaphakade.’’"
  40,65,"Yena Uphila ngonaphakade, akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaKhe, ngoko thandazani kuYe, ninyanisekile kuYe enkolweni, iindumiso zonke mazibe kuAllâh iNkosi yamaphakade"
  40,66,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Inene mna ndalelwa ukuba ndinqule abo nibanqulayo ngaphandle koAllâh, nje ukufika kwemiqondiso evela eNkosini yam, kwaye mna ndiyalelwe ukuba ndizinikele eNkosini yamaphakade.’’"
  40,67,"Nguye Owanidalayo ngothuli, emva koko ngeqabaza lembewu yomntu, emva koko ngehlwili elinamathelayo; emva koko Unikhuphela ngaphandle ningabantwana, Aphinde Aniphucule nifikelele ebuntwini, Niphinde nibe ngamaxhego. Ukanti phakathi kwenu kukho abo bathatyathwa bafe phambi (koko) khona ukuze nifikelele kwithuba elithile; mhlawumbi niya kuyisebenzisa ingqiqo"
  40,68,"NguYe Onika ubomi Enze ukufa; Xa Emisela into Usuka Athi kuyo: “Yibakho”, ibekho"
  40,69,Akubaboni na ukuba baphambuke njani na abo baphikisana nemiqondiso ka-Allâh
  40,70,Abo bayiphikayo iNcwadi (i’Kur’ân) noko Sakuthumela abaThunywa beThu baza kwazi
  40,71,Xa amakhamandela ebathandele ezintanyeni zabo namakhonkco; baya kurhuqwa
  40,72,Emanzini abilayo; naseMlilweni baya kuhlohlwa (amadangatya oMlilo eziswini zabo)
  40,73,"Kuze kuthiwe kubo: “Baphi na abo nanidla ngokubayamanisa njengamahlulelane (kuAllâh)"
  40,74,"bengengo-Allâh?’’ Baya kuthi bona: “Basishiyile: gxebe, asizanga sinqule nto thina ngaphambili,” Ubalahlekisa ngolo hlobo ke uAllâh abangakholwayo"
  40,75,"(Iingelosi ziya kuthi): “Oko kwaba ngenxa yokuba nina nanizikhukhumalisa emhlabeni ngokungekho lungelweni yaye naniziphethe ngolunya"
  40,76,"NgenanikeemasangweniesiHogonihlaleaphongonaphakade, hayi ukungcola kwendawo yokuhlala izikhukhumali!”"
  40,77,"Ngoko ke wena (Muhammad) yiba nomonde; inene isithembiso sika-Allâh siyinyaniso. Enokuba Singakubonisa inxalenye yoko Sibathembise kona okanye Sikuthabathe wena ngokufa, kukuThi apho baza kubuyiselwa khona"
  40,78,"Ke kaloku Sanithumela abaThunywa ngaphambi kwenu. Phakathi kwabo kukho abo (iimbali zabo) sele Sikubalisele ngazo, kuze phakathi kwabo kubekho abo (iimbali zabo) Singakubaliselanga ngazo. Kananjalo yayingekokwakhe nawuphi na uMthunywa ukuba eze nomqondiso (okanye iVesi) ngaphandle kwemvume ka-Allâh. Ngoko ke xa umyalelo ka-Allâh ufika uya kufezekiswa ngenyaniso baze abaqambi bobuxoki balahlekelwe"
  40,79,"NguAllâh Owanenzela izilwanyana ezidla ingca eniziqabelayo, ukanti ezinye zazo niyazidla"
  40,80,"Ukanti kwalapho kuzo nineenzuzo (ezizezinye) kanti kwalapho kuzo nifezekisa iimfuno ezisezifubeni5 zenu, ukanti zona neenqanawa ziyanithwala"
  40,81,Ke kaloku Yena Unibonise imiqondiso yaKhe ngoko ke yiyiphi le miqondiso ka-Allâh niyiphikayo
  40,82,"Kanti abakahamba-hambi na ehlabathini babone ukuba sabanjani na isiphelo sabo babandulelayo? babebaninzi ngakumbi kunabo, benamandla nomfaneleko ngakumbi kunabo ehlabathini, kodwa azanga bancedakale koko bakusebenzelayo"
  40,83,"Kananjalo ukufika kwabaThunywa babo kubo nobungqina obucacileyo, (basuka) bagutyungelwa koko babekugculela"
  40,84,"Ke kaloku bakubona isohlwayo seThu, bathi: “Sikholwa kuAllâhYedwathina,asikholwakokobesikadesikwayamanisa naYe.”"
  40,85,"Kodwa aluzanga ukholo lwabo lubancede (nto), ukubonana kwabo nesohlwayo seThu. (Sona) yindlela eyamiselwayo ka-Allâh Aqubisana ngayo nezicaka zaKhe. Apho ke abangakholwayo balahlekelwa (yinto yonke)"
  41,1,Hâ Mîm
  41,2,"(Esi siTyhilelo) sivela (kuAllâh), uSolubabalo, uSozinceba"
  41,3,"INcwadi eVesi zayo zichazwe ngengcombolo, i’Kur’ân yesiArabhu kubantu abanolwazi"
  41,4,"Ingumniki weendaba ezivuyisayo ikwangumlumkisi; kodwa abaninzi kubo bayatshikila, ngoko ke abeva"
  41,5,"Kananjalo bathi: “Iintliziyo zethu ziphantsi kwezigqubuthelo malunga noko usimemela kuko, yaye ezindlebeni zethu kukho ubuthulu, kunjalo nje phakathi kwethu nani kukho umsantsa, ngoko ke sebenza wena nathi siyasebenza.”"
  41,6,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Mna ndingumntu njengani ekutyhilwe kuye okokuba uThixo wenu nguThixo oMnye; ngoko ke thabathani iNdlela ethe Ngqo eya kuYe, nicele itarhu kuYe. ‘’Kananjalo yeha kwabo bayamanisa abanye kuAllâh"
  41,7,"Abo banganikeliyo ngeZakâh, bona kuBomi belizayo abakholwa"
  41,8,"Inene bona abo bakholwayo, benze izenzo ezilungileyo okwabo ngumvuzo ongenakuphazamiseka"
  41,9,"Yithi: “Ingaba ngenene anikholwa kuloWo Wadala umhlaba ngeentsuku ezimbini, nayamanisa (abanye kuYe) nithi bayalingana naYe? Leyo yiNkosi yamaphakade"
  41,10,"Yena ke Wabeka kuwo (umhlaba) iintaba zema ngokuqinileyo phezu kwawo, Wathoba iintsikelelo phezu kwawo, Wenza umlinganiselo wezinto zonke, Wabonelela (izidalwa) zawo ngesixhaso ngeentsuku ezine ezilinganayo, kwabo babuzayo"
  41,11,"Waza Yena Wabhekisa ngasezulwini lo gama lalingumsi Wathi kulo nasemhlabeni: “Yibanikho, nithanda okanye ningathandi.” Lathi (lona izulu nomhlaba): “Sizile (yaye sikho) sithanda.”"
  41,12,"Ke kaloku Wawafezekisa (amazulu) angamazulu asixhenxe ngeentsuku ezimbini Waphefumlela izulu ngalinye umyalelo walo kananjalo Salihombisa izulu elikufutshane ngezibane (Ukuba zibe ngumhombiso) nokhuseleko. Lowo ngummiselo waKhe uSomandla, uSolwazi"
  41,13,"Ke kaloku ukuba bayatshikila, yithi wena (Muhmmad): “Mna ndinilumkisile ngokugqekreza kwezulu, okunje ngokugqekreza kwezulu (okwabetha) ama’Ad namaThamûd"
  41,14,"(Oko kwenzeka) kusakuba kwakufike abaThunywa kubo, phambi kwabo nasemva kwabo, (besithi), “Musani ukunqula nto ngaphandle koAllâh.” Bathi bona (abangakholwayo): “Ukuba iNkosi yethu Ibithandile, ngeYithumele iingelosi, inene thina koko nikuthunyiweyo asikholwa.”"
  41,15,"Abakwa’Ad bona babekhukhumele emhlabeni ngokungekho lungelweni, besithi: “Ngubani na onamandla kunathi?” Babengayicingi na bona into yokuba uAllâh Owabadalayo Wayenamandla kakhulu kunabo? Ke bona baye bayala imiqondiso yeThu"
  41,16,Thina Sathumela umoya otswinayo ngeemini zeshwangusha ukubenza bangcamle isohlwayo sehlazo kobu bomi; kodwa sona isohlwayo selizayo sihlazisa ngakumbi yaye abayi kuncedwa
  41,17,"AbakwaThamûd, bona Sabakhokela, kodwa bakhetha ubumfama ngaphezu kwesiKhokelo, ngoko ke isithonga sezulu esisisohlwayo esinyelisayo sabahlasela ngoko bakwenzayo"
  41,18,"Ke kaloku Sabasindisa abo bakholwayo, bamoyikayo uAllâh"
  41,19,(Bachazele Muhammad) nangeMini iintshaba zika-Allâh ziya kuqundaniswa eMlilweni lo gama baya (kuqhutyelwa kuwo) bengamaqela aya kuba ngemigca
  41,20,"De bafike kuWo (uMlilo), ukuva kwabo (iindlebe), amehlo abo nezikhumba zabo ziya kungqina ngokuchasene nabo ngoko bakwenzayo"
  41,21,"Baya kuthi kwizikhumba zabo: “Kutheni na ningqina ngokuchasene nathi nje?’’ Ziya kuthi zona: “Senziwe okokuba sithethe, nguAllâh Owenze yonke into yathetha. Yena Wanidala okokuqala, (ngoko ke) nibuyiselwa kuYe"
  41,22,"Ke kaloku nina naningazigqumi (nenzele) ukuba hleze ukuva kwenu kungqine ngokuchasene nani okanye ukubona kwenu okanye izikhumba zenu, koko nina naye nacinga ukuba uAllâh Akakwazi kakhulu enikwenzayo"
  41,23,"Ezo ke yayiziingcinga zenu enazicingayo ngeNkosi yenu. Zinifake entshabalalweni ke (ngoku), yaye nisuke naba ngabanye babalahlekelwa.”"
  41,24,"Kanti ke nokuba bangaba nomonde, uMlilo yindawo yabo yokuhlala; naxa becela ukuzicengezelela (kuAllâh), abayi kuba ngabanye babo bavunyelwayo ukuba bazicengezelele"
  41,25,"Ke kaloku Sabanyulela abahlobo abenza okungaphambili (kwamehlo) abo kwaba nomtsalane nokwakungemva kwabo (kusisono), ke lona ilizwi (lommiselo) liyasebenza kwizizwe ezadlulayo ngaphambi kwabo kwiijinni nakubantu. Inene bona bonke baba ngabalahlekelwa"
  41,26,"Abo bangakholwayo bathi: “Musani ukuyiphulaphula le ‘Kur’ân yaye thethani ngengxolo xa (icengcelezwayo) mhlawumbi niya kuba noloyiso.’’"
  41,27,"Kodwa Thina inene Siya kwenza abo bangakholwayo bangcamle isohlwayo esibuhlungu, kwaye Siya kuba buyekeza ngokwenene ngoko kubi bakwenzayo"
  41,28,Le yimbuyekezo yeentshaba zika-Allâh uMlilo. Elabo ikhaya lanaphakade (liya) kuba phakathi (eMlilweni) apho njengembuyekezo yoko kuziiVesi zeThu bazalayo
  41,29,"Kananjalo abo bangakholwayo baya kuthi : “Nkosi yethu, sibonise abo basilahlekisayo kwiijinni nabantu (ukuze) sibabeke phantsi kweenyawo zethu, babe kunye nabo bangaphantsi.”"
  41,30,"Inene abo bathi (kwangaphambili): “INkosi yethu nguAllâh, bahlala eNdleleni elungileyo iingelosi ziya kuhla phezu kwabo, (zisithi): “Ningoyiki ninganxunguphali koko yamkelani iindaba ezivuyisayo zePaladesi enanithenjiswe ngayo"
  41,31,"Thina zingelosi sasingamadlelane enu kubomi basemhlabeni. Yaye nina niya kufumana konke oko kunqwenelwa yimiphefumlo yenu, yaye niya kukufumana konke apho enikucelayo"
  41,32,"UbuBele obuvela (kuYe) uMxoleli, uSozinceba.”"
  41,33,"Ngubani na ontetho yakhe ingcono ukugqitha lowo umemela kuAllâh, enze okulungileyo, athi: “Inene mna ndingomnye wamaMuslim.”"
  41,34,Azifani izenzo ezilungileyo nezimbi. Guzula (okungcolileyo) ngokulungileyo; kulapho kanye lowo phakathi kwakho naye kukho ubutshaba aza kuba ngathi ngumhlobo wakho osenyongweni
  41,35,"Kodwa ke akukho bani ukuphiwayo oko ngaphandle kwabo banomonde, akukho bani ukuphiweyo oko ngaphandle kwalowo unesahlulo esikhulu (sokulungileyo entliziyweni yakhe)"
  41,36,"KekalokuxaufikelwayingcebisoengcolileyoivelakuShaytân; cela ukhuseleko ngoAllâh. Inene Yena nguSokuva, uSolwazi"
  41,37,"Phakathi kwemiqondiso yaKhe kukho ubusuku nemini, ilanga nenyanga, ke wena uze ungaqubudi elangeni nokuba kusenyangeni na, koko wena qubuda kuAllâh, Owazidalayo, ukuba nguYe omnqulayo wena"
  41,38,Ukuba bakhukhumele ke abo basondeleyo eNkosini yakho bona (iingelosi) bayaMzukisa (uAllâh) ubusuku nemini yaye abadinwa
  41,39,"Kananjalo phakathi kwemiqondiso yaKhe kukuba uye uwubone umhlaba uludlolo, kodwa Sisakuthulula imvula phezu kwawo, uvuseleleke ukhule (uhlaza) Inene, Yena loWo Uwunika ubomi, inene Uyakwazi ukunika ubomi kwabafileyo. Inene Yena Unamandla ngaphezu kweento zonke"
  41,40,"Inene abo bafakela ukuphambuka kwiiVesi zeThu abafihlakelanga kuThi, Ingaba lowo uphoswe eMlilweni ungcono okanye ngulowo uya kubuya esindile na ngoMhla woVuko? Yenzani enikuthandayo, inene Yena Uyakubona oko nikwenzayo"
  41,41,Inene abo bangakholwayo kwinkumbuzo (i’Kur’ân) emveni kokuba ifikile kubo (baya kuzuza isohlwayo) kananjalo inene yona iyiNcwadi enamandla
  41,42,"Ubuxoki abunakusondela kuyo, enokuba buvela ngaphambili kuyo okanye ngemva kwayo na; isisiTyhilelo esivela kuYe OsiSilumko, Wokudunyiswa"
  41,43,"Akukho nto ethethwayo kuwe (Muhammad) engazanga ithethwekubaThunywaabakwandulelayo, IneneiNkosiyakho nguMnini kuxolela IkwanguMnini sohlwayo esibuhlungu"
  41,44,"Ke kaloku ukuba ngaba beSiyenze yaba yi’Kur’ân yasemzini1 bebeza kuthi: “Kutheni na iiVesi zayo zingacaciswanga ngengcombolo (ngolwimi lwethu) nje? Sisicengcelezo sasemzini na (esi) nomProfeti ongumArabhu kusini na?” Yithi wena : “(Le ‘Kur’ân) sisiKhokelo nokuphilisa kwabo bakholwayo, ke bona abo bangakholwayo ezindlebeni zabo kukho ubuthulu, yaye banobumfama (emehlweni abo); Bona abo (beva kaluzizi ngathi) babizwa kwindawo ekude"
  41,45,"Kananjalo Sanika uMûsâ isiBhalo, kodwa kwabakho ukuphikisana ngaso. Ke kaloku ukuba kwakungekho ngenxa yelizwi (lommiselo) elalisele liphumile livela eNkosini yakho kwangaphambili, ngekuba umcimbi sele wagqitywa phakathi kwabo. Kodwa inene bona baneentandabuzo ngayo (i’Kur’ân)"
  41,46,Nabani na lowo wenza okulungileyo wenzela umphefumlo wakhe; nabani na lowo wenza okungcolileyo (ukwenza oko) ngokuchasene naye. Ke Yona iNkosi yakho Ayinantswela- bulungisa kwizicaka zayo
  41,47,"KukuYe kuphela apho ulwazi lweYure lulindelekileyo. Kananjalo iziqhamo aziphumi kumaqokobhe azo, kungekho mazi izalayo ingazali ngolwazi lwaKhe. Ke kaloku ngeMini Aya kukhwaza kubo (Athi) : “Aphi na amahlulelane aM?’’ Baya kuthi bona, “Thina sikwazisa ukuba akusekho naliphi na ingqina phakathi kwethu2’’ (elazi loo nto)"
  41,48,"Abaya kunyamalala kubo ngabo babedla ngokucela kubo ngaphambili, yaye baya kuba besazi ngokuqinisekileyo okokuba abayi kuba nandawo yakuphuncula (esohlwayweni sika-Allâh)"
  41,49,"Umntu akadinwa kukuthandaza acele (izinto) ezilungileyo, kodwa esakuchukunyiswa kokubi, ulahlekelwa lithemba athi khulubembe"
  41,50,"Ze kuthi xa Simenze wangcamla inceba evela kuThi emva kwenkxwaleko ebikhe yamfumana, asuke athi: “Oku kuziimfanelo zam, yaye andiqondi ukuba iYure iya kuhla kanti naxa ndibuyiselwa eNkosini yam, inene okwam okukuYo kuya kuba kokona kulungileyo.” Kodwa Thina Siya kubaxelela abo babengakholwa ngoko bakwenzayo, kwaye Siya kubenza bangcamle isohlwayo esikhulu"
  41,51,"Kananjalo Sithi Sisakubonelela umntu ngobuBele, asuke atshikile, achaselele phayaa; kodwa esakufunyanwa bububi aqale enze imilembelele emide yemithandazo"
  41,52,"Yithi: “Niyayibona na ukuba le ‘Kur’ân ivela kuAllâh kodwa anikholwa kuyo, ngubani na olahleke ngakumbi ukugqitha lowo usekuphikiseni (icebo lika-Allâh)"
  41,53,Siya kubabonisa imiqondiso yeThu ke elundini nakubo buqu kude kucace kubo ukuba (i’Kur’ân) iyinyaniso. Kanti akwanelanga na ukuba (nazi) ngeNkosi yenu ukuba Yona IliNgqina ngaphezu kweento zonke
  41,54,"Yeha, basezintandabuzweni ngendibano neNkosi yabo, yeha Yona Irhangqele izinto zonke"
  42,1,Hâ-Mim
  42,2,"‘Ayn,-Sîn-’Kâf"
  42,3,"Utyhile ngolo hlobo ke kuwe (Muhammad) nakwabo bangaphambili kunawe uAllâh, uSobunganga, uSobulumko"
  42,4,"KokwaKhe okusemazulwini nokusemhlabeni, kwaye Uphakamile Yena, Mkhulu"
  42,5,"Amazulu aphantsela ukucandeka emantla kwawo kanti neengelosi zizukisa (uAllâh) ngendumiso yeNkosi yazo, zicelela abo basemhlabeni itarhu. Inene nguAllâh OnguMxoleli, uSozinceba"
  42,6,"Bona abo bazithabathela abahlobo abangabanye ngaphandle kwaKhe uAllâh UsenguMlondolozi wabo, ke wena (Muhammad) akungomlawuli wabo"
  42,7,"Ngoko ke Thina Sityhile i’Kur’ân yesiArabhu khona ukuze ulumkise uNozala wezixeko (iMakkah) nezo (zixeko) zimngqongileyo, ulumkise kananjalo ngeMini yeNdibano, ekungekho ntandabuzo ngayo. Elinye iqela liya kuba sePaladesi lize elinye iqela libe seDangatyeni"
  42,8,"Ukanti ukuba uAllâh Ebethanda, Ebengabenza babe kwiNkolo enye, kodwa ke Yena Ungenisa lowo Athande ukumngenisa kwiNceba yaKhe. Bona ke abenzi bobubi abanamkhuseli bengenaye namncedi"
  42,9,"Makube mhlawumbi bazithabathele bakhuseli bambi ngaphandle kwaKhe? Kodwa uAllâh Yena nguMkhuseli, yaye Unika ubomi kwabafileyo, ukanti Yena Unamandla ngaphezulu kunezinto zonke"
  42,10,"Ke kaloku nantoni na eningangqinelaniyo ngayo isigwebo sayo sibhekiseni kuAllâh. (Yithi): “Lowo nguAllâh, iNkosi yam; kukuYe apho ndithembele khona, kukuYe nalapho ndiza kubuyela khona.”"
  42,11,"UMdali wamazulu nomhlaba, Wanenzela abalingane benu Ebakhupha kwiziqu zenu, nezilwanyana eziyimfuyo yenu Wazenzela abalingane bazo, Aze ngale ndlela Anandise, akukho nto ifana naYe, yaye Yena nguSokuva, uSokubona"
  42,12,"ZezaKhe izitshixo zamazulu nomhlaba, Wandisela, isixhaso lowo Athandileyo Aze Amenzele umlinganiselo wakhe, Inene Yena Unolwazi ngaphezu kweento zonke"
  42,13,"Yena Umisele kwinkolo yenu oko Wakuyalela uNûh noko Sikutyhile kuwe (Muhammad), noko Sakuyalela kuIbrâhîm noMûsâ no’Isâ ukumisela inkolo, hayi ukwenza iyantlukwano kuyo. Okunzima kwabo bayamanisa abanye kuAllâh koko ubamemela kuko. uAllâh Uzikhethela lowo Athande ukuzikhethela yena, Akhokelele kuYe lowo ubuyela kuYe (ngenguquko)"
  42,14,"Ke kaloku abazanga babe neyantlukwano de kwaba semva kokufika kolwazi kubo ngenxa yomona nobutshaba phakathi kwabo. Yaye ukuba kwakungekho ngenxa yelizwi esele laphumayo livela eNkosini yakho (ukulibazisa ukufika kwesohlwayo) kude kube lixesha, elimisiweyo, umcimbi ngowusele wagqitywa kudala phakathi kwabo. Kananjalo inene abo babenikwe ilifa lesiBhalo emva kwabo mayela naso baba neentandabuzo ezimandla"
  42,15,"Ngoko ke wena memela abantu kuloo (nkolo ka-Allâh) uhlale useNdleleni ethe Tye njengoko uyalelwe, ungalandeli (izinto) abakekelele ngakuzo koko wena yithi : “Mna ndikholwe koko kutyhilwe nguAllâh kwisiBhalo (i’Kur’ân), yaye ndiyalelwe ukuba ndenze ubulungisa phakathi kwenu. UAllâh yiNkosi yethu ekwayiNkosi yenu. Thina sinezenzo zethu nani ninezenzo zenu akukho ngxoxo phakathi kwethu nani. UAllâh Uza kusibuyisela (kuye) sonke yaye kukuye apho isiphelo sohambo sikhoyo.”"
  42,16,"Abo baphikisana (nabakholwayo) ngoAllâh emveni kokuba sele Amkelwe, ukuphikisa kwabo akunto yanto kwiNkosi yabo, yaye phezu kwabo kukho ingqumbo (yaKhe) kwaye okwabo sisohlwayo esibuhlungu"
  42,17,NguAllâh Othumele iNcwadi ngenyaniso kunye nesikali (sokwahlula ubulungisa nentswela-bulungisa). Ingaba yintoni na enokwenza uqiqe? Mhlawumbi iYure sele ikufuphi
  42,18,"Abo bangakholwayo kuyo abanamonde ngayo, kodwa bona abo bakholwayo bayayoyika, besazi okokuba iyinyaniso. Yeha abo bayiphikayo iYure basekulahlekeni kokwenene"
  42,19,UAllâh UnobuBele kwizicaka zaKhe; Unika imbonelelo kulowo Athande ukumnika. Yaye Yena nguSomandla uSobunganga
  42,20,"Lowo unqwenela isivuno soBomi oBuzayo Siyamandisela isivuno (somvuzo). Ke lowo unqwenela isivuno seli hlabathi Siyamnika sona eso, kodwa akayi kuba nasabelo kuBomi oBuzayo"
  42,21,"Okanye mhlawumbi banamahlulelane abayalele ukuba babe nenkolo uAllâh Anganikanga mvume ngayo? Ukuba bekungekho ngenxa yelizwi elicacileyo, ngowusele wagqitywa kudala umcimbi phakathi kwabo. Inene abenzi bobubi baya kufumana isohlwayo esibuhlungu"
  42,22,"Uza kubabona abenzi bobubi besoyika oko bakusebenzelayo yaye (isohlwayo sika-Allâh) siza kubahlela. Ke bona abo bakholwayo baya kuba kumacandelo obumnandi ePaladesi, befumana yonke into abathande ukuyifumana phambi kweNkosi yabo. Oko koko kububuBele obukhulu"
  42,23,"Oko kukuba uAllâh Anike iindaba ezivuyisayo kwizicaka zaKheezikholwayozezenzoezilungileyo.Yithi(Muhammad): “Andinihlawulisi nento le (ngalo myalezo) koko kukulunga kuphela kwizizalwana, kanti ke nabani na owenza isenzo esilungileyo Siya kumongezelela okulungileyo kuso apho. Inene uAllâh nguMxoleli, Uyabulela"
  42,24,"Okanye bathi: “(UMuhammad) uqambe ubuxoki ngoAllâh?’’ kodwa ukuba uAllâh Ebethanda Ebengasuka ayitywine intliziyo yakho, yaye uAllâh Uyabutshabalalisa ubuxoki Amisele inyaniso ngelizwi laKhe. Inene, Yena nguSolwazi woko kusezifubeni"
  42,25,"Nguye Owamkela inguquko kwizicaka zaKhe Axolele nezenzo ezigwenxa, yaye Uyakwazi enikwenzayo"
  42,26,"Kwaye Uyayiphendula imithandazo yabo bakholwayo (kuYe), benze izenzo zobulungisa, Abongezelele ubuBele baKhe. Kodwa bona abangakholwayo baya kufumana isohlwayo esibi kunene"
  42,27,"Ukuba ngaba uAllâh Wayezandisele iimbonelelo (zonke) izicaka zaKhe, zaziya kwenza ingcinezelo ehlabathini. Kodwa Yena Uthulula umlinganiselo Athande ukuthulula wona. Inene Yena Uyazazi izicaka zaKhe Uyabona"
  42,28,"Nguye Othoba imvula emva kokuphelelwa kwabo lithemba, Aze Asasaze inceba yaKhe, kaloku Yena nguMkhuseli, Ufanelwe kukudunyiswa"
  42,29,Kananjalo omnye wemiqondiso yaKhe kukudalwa kwamazulu nomhlaba noko Akusasaze kuwo kuzizidalwa. Ukanti kukuYe ukuziqokelela ndawonye xa Ethandile kulula
  42,30,"Ke kaloku nantoni na enihlelayo engumonakalo oko koko kwenziwa zizandla zenu, kodwa Yena Uxolela kakhulu"
  42,31,Kanti ke aniyi kumenza Asilele (uAllâh) emhlabeni. Yaye aninawumbi umkhuseli ngaphandle koAllâh
  42,32,Kananjalo omnye wemiqondiso yaKhe ziinqanawa elwandle ezingathi ziintaba
  42,33,"Ukuba Ebethanda Yena Ebengawumisa (ngxishi) umoya, zize (ezo nqanawa) zingahambi (elwandle). Inene kuko oko kukho imiqondiso kuye nabani na onomonde, onombulelo"
  42,34,Kungenjalo Ebengasuka Abatshabalalise ngenxa yoko bakwenzayo (kuzizono); kodwa Yena uxolela kakhulu
  42,35,Abo banamaphike ngemiqondiso yeThu mabazi (kakuhle) okokuba abayi kuba nandawo yakuphuncula (esohlwayweni sika-Allâh)
  42,36,Ke kaloku nantoni na eniyinikwayo (loo nto) yeyolonwabo lobomi basemhlabeni. Kodwa oko kuku-Allâh kukona kuthabatha ixesha elide kwabo bakholwayo babeke ithemba labo eNkosini yabo
  42,37,Abo baziphephayo izono zabo nezenzo zokungcola bathi xa benomsindo baxolele
  42,38,"Nabo baye basabela eNkosini yabo, benza iSalah nabasombulula imicimbi yabo ngemboniswano phakathi kwabo, banikele (kumalizo) oko Sibanike kona"
  42,39,Nabo bathi xa bethwaxwe yingcinezelo bazikhusele
  42,40,"Ke kaloku imbuyekezo yesenzo esingcolileyo sisenzo esingcole ngokufana naso kodwa ke lowo uxolelayo, enze noxolelwaniso umvuzo wakhe ukuAllâh. Inene Yena Akabathandi abenzi bobubi"
  42,41,"Kananjalo lowo uziphindezelayo emva kokuba enziwe ubugwenxa, kwabo banjalo akukho sizathu (sakusoleka)"
  42,42,Isizathu (sokusoleka) sikulowo wona abantu enze ingcinezelo emhlabeni engenalungelo. Abenza (oko) baya kufumana isohlwayo esibuhlungu
  42,43,"Lowo unyamezelayo, axolele inene oko yenye yezinto (ezibonakalisa) ukuzinikela (kakhulu kuAllâh)"
  42,44,"Ke lowo uAllâh amyekele ekulahlekeni akuyi kubakho mkhuseli kuye ngaphaya kwaKhe (uAllâh), kananjalo uya kubabona abenzi bobubi xa bebona isohlwayo baya kuthi: “Ingaba ikhona na indlela yokubuyela (ehlabathini) kwakhona"
  42,45,"Kantiuzakubabonabesondezwakuwo(uMlilo), bethotyiselwa ngokuhlazeka, belaqaza, ngomnqweno. Abo bakholwayo baya kuthi: “Inene abona balahlekelwa bokwenyani ngabo balahlekelwe ziziqu zabo neentsapho zabo ngeMini yoVuko, Yeha, abenzi bobubi bakwisohlwayo esingapheliyo.”"
  42,46,Kananjalo abayi kuba namhlobo wakubanceda ngaphandle koAllâh. Yaye lowo uyekelwe nguAllâh ekulahlekeni akukho ndlela kuye
  42,47,"Sabelani eNkosini yenu ingekafiki iMini evela kuAllâh ekungekhe kubekho nto iyigxothayo. Akukho lukhuseleko niya kulufumana ngaloo Mini, kungayi kubakho kuphika kuni"
  42,48,"Kanti ukuba bayatshikila Thina Asikuthumelanga kubo ukuba ube ngumlondolozi wabo, okwakho wena kukuvakalisa, ke kaloku xa Sithe Senza umntu wangcamla inceba evela kuThi, uye ayivuyele, kodwa athi xa ububi bumthwaxa ngenxa yoko kuvezwe zizandla zakhe inene umntu angabi nambulelo"
  42,49,"Loluka-Allâh ulongamelo lwamazulu nomhlaba. Yena Udala loo nto Athande ukuyidala. Anike lowo Athande ukumnika (abantwana) abaziintombi, Anike lowo Athande ukumnika amakhwenkwe"
  42,50,"Kungenjalo Abenzele amakhwenkwe neentombi, Enze udlolo lowo Athande ukumenza, Inene Yena nguSolwazi, uSomandla"
  42,51,"Kananjalo asikokwakhe nawuphi na umntu ukuba uAllâh Athethe naye ngaphandle kokuthetha naye ngesiTyhilelo okanye ngaphaya komkhusane okanye Athumele isiThunywa simtyhilelengemvumeyaKheokoAthandeukuba(Amtyhilele kona). Inene Yena Uphakamile, Unobulumko"
  42,52,"sisityhile ngolo hlobo ke isiTyhhilelo somyalelo weThu (i’Kur’ân). Wena wawungazi siBhalo, (ungalwazi) ukholo kodwa ke Thina Sisenze (isiBhalo) saba lukhanyiselo eSikhokela ngalo lowo Sithande ukumkhokela kwizicaka zeThu. Kwaye inene wena (Muhammad) ukhokelela eNdleleni ethe Tye"
  42,53,INdlela ka-Allâh (loWo) izezaKhe zonke (izinto) ezisemazulwini nasemhlabeni. Yeha! KukuAllâh apho zonke izinto ziza kubuyela khona
  43,1,Hâ-Mim
  43,2,(Ndifunga) ngeNcwadi (i’Kur’ân) ecacileyo
  43,3,"Inene, Siyenze yayi’Kur’ân engesiArabhu khon’ukuze nibe nokuyiva (intsingiselo yayo)"
  43,4,"Kananjalo yona ikuNozala weNcwadi1 okuThi, ixabisekile, izele bubulumko"
  43,5,"Siwuhluthe na umyalezo kuni, Sinigxothe ngokuba ningabantu abagabadele batsiba imida"
  43,6,Kodwa bangaphi abaProfeti eSabathumela phakathi kwabantu bamandulo
  43,7,Ukanti akukho Mprofeti wakha wafika kubo bangamgculeli
  43,8,"Sabatshabalalisa ke Thina, ababenamandla ngaphezulu kunabo, (nabo) baba ngumzekelo wabantu ababandulelayo"
  43,9,"Kanti xa unokubabuza: “Ngubani owadala amazulu nomhlaba?’’ Inene baza kukuxelela okokuba: “Adalwa nguSobunganga, uSolwazi.”"
  43,10,Owanenzela umhlaba waba ngumandlalo wenu ekukho iindlela eninokuthi nikhokeleleke ngazo
  43,11,"Othumela imvula phantsi ivela esibhakabhakeni ingemilinganiselo eqingqiweyo, ke kaloku ngayo Sivuselela umhlaba ofileyo niya kuvuswa ngolo hlobo ke nani"
  43,12,"Yena loWo Wadalela zonke izinto amaqabane azo, Wanenzela iinqanawa neenkomo (namahashe) eniye niziqabele (nihambe ngazo)"
  43,13,"Khona ukuze nihlale emihlana yazo nikhumbule uBabalo lweNkosi yenu, xa nihlala phezu kwazo nisithi: “Uzuko malube kuloWo Wenze esi (sithuthi) saba phantsi kolawulo lwethu, (ngapha koko) besingekhe sisoyise"
  43,14,Yaye kananjalo eNkosini yethu kulapho siza kubuyela khona.”
  43,15,"Kodwa (ngoko kunjalo) babalela kuYe isahlulo esingabanye kwizicaka zaKhe, inene umntu akanambulelo"
  43,16,"Okanye Yena (uAllâh), Uzithabathele koko Wakudalayo, iintombi Waza nina Wanikhethela oonyana kusini na"
  43,17,"Ke kaloku xa omnye kubo enikwa iindaba ezimnandi zoko akubalela kuSozinceba, ubuso bakhe, buyafiphala, azicinezele kukukhathazeka kwakhe"
  43,18,"Ingaba lowo ukhuliswe ngezihombiso5, ongakwazi kuyicacisa into ayithethayo ngexesha lembambano, (ubalelwa kuAllâh)"
  43,19,"Kananjalo benze iingelosi ezizizicaka zikaSozinceba zaba ngabasetyhini, babekhona na ukudalwa kwazo? Ubungqina babo buza kubhalwa phantsi yaye baza kubuzwa"
  43,20,"Kananjalo bathi (xa bezithethelela bodwa): “Ukuba uSozinceba Ebengathandanga, besingekhe sizinqule (ezi zithixo zethu).’’ Akukho lwazi banalo mayela noko, abakwenzayo kukuqamba ubuxoki"
  43,21,"Okanye kukho incwadi eSibanike yona mhlawumbi phambi kwayo (i’Kur’ân), ekuyiyona babambelele kuyo"
  43,22,"Ngapha koko bathi: “Inene thina safumana oobawo besenkolweni (ethile) thina ke silandela ezinyaweni zabo, sisendleleni (elungileyo).’’"
  43,23,"Ngokukwanjalo ke Thina Asizanga Sathumela Mlumkisi kuso nasiphi na isixeko baze abazizityebi baso bangathi: “Inene thina safumana oobawo bethu besenkolweni, silandela ezinyaweni zabo ke thina.”"
  43,24,"(UMlumkisi ngamnye) wathi (ebantwini): “Nokuba ndiniphathele isiKhokelo esingcono kuneso (siyiloo nkolo) nafumana ooyihlo bekuso?’’ Bathi bona: “Inene thina koko nikuthunyiweyo asikholwa.’’"
  43,25,Sathabatha impindezelo ke Thina kubo; khawubone ke ukuba saba njani na isiphelo sabaphikisi
  43,26,"Yabona xa uIbrâhîm wathi kuyise nakubantu bakubo: “Inene mna ndiyazikhwebula koko nikunqulayo"
  43,27,"Ngaphandle kwaloWo Wandidalayo, yaye Yena Uya kundikhokela.’’"
  43,28,Kananjalo oko wakwenza kwaba lilizwi elashiyeka phakathi kwenzala yakhe ukwenzela ukuba babe nokubuyela (eNdleleni)
  43,29,"Ke kaloku Mna (Allâh) Ndanika aba bantu abangabanquli zithixo ubomi bolonwabo, nooyise kwada kwafika inyaniso noMthunywa ocacileyo (uMuhammad)"
  43,30,"Kodwa yathi inyaniso isakufika kubo bathi bona: “Ngumlingo lo, yaye thina asikholwa kuwo.’’"
  43,31,"Bathi kananjalo: “Kutheni le ‘Kur’ân ingathunyelwanga kweyona ndoda inkulu (kwesinye) sezixeko ezibini"
  43,32,"Bangabahlula-hluli benceba yeNkosi yakho na? Sithi nje Ababakhethele indlela yokuphila kubomi beli hlabathi, Saphakamisa abanye babo bangentla kwabanye ngokwamabakala khona ukuze bakwazi ukusebenzisana ngokwengqesho. Kodwa inceba yeNkosi yakho yiyona ingcono ngaphezu kwako konke abakuwanqayo"
  43,33,"Ukuba ibingekuko okokuba abantu bebengasuka babe luluntu olunye (lwabantu abangakholwayo) beSiza kwenzela abo bangakholwayo kuSozinceba imizi yabo iisilinga, nemichankcatho, yesilivere yokunyuka"
  43,34,"Nezindlu zabo (zibe) neengcango, neesofa zokungqiyama"
  43,35,Nezihombiso zegolide. Kodwa konke oko akunto yanto ngaphandle kokuba zizinto zolonwabo zobomi balo mhlaba. Ukanti uBomi oBuzayo bona obukuAllâh bobabenzi bokulungileyo
  43,36,Lowo umfanyekisiweyo mayela nenkumbulo kaSozinceba Simnyulela uShaytân ukuba abe ngumhlobo wakhe
  43,37,Inene wona (amashayâtini) ayaphambukisa eNdleleni (yesiKhokelo) logama bona bezicingela ukuba bangabakhokelelekileyo (baseNdleleni)
  43,38,"Ade (umntu) afike kuThi (ngeMini yoMgwebo), athi: “O, akwaba kwakubekho umgama ongangophakathi kwempuma nentshona phakathi kwethu, ungonjani ukungcola yena umhlobo.”"
  43,39,"Kubekungasayikuncedanto(ukutsholoomazwi) ngaloo Mini, emveni kokuba sele nonile, sele nisabelana ngesohlwayo"
  43,40,Ingaba (Muhammad) uza kuyikhokela imfama okanye lowo usekulahlekeni okucacileyo
  43,41,"Enokuba Singakuthabatha (ngokufa), inene Thina Siza kuthabatha impindezelo kubo"
  43,42,"Kanti nokuba Singakubonisa na oko Sibathembise kona (kusisohlwayo), inene Thina Sigqibelele ukwazi ukwenza"
  43,43,Ngoko ke wena bambelela koko kutyhilwe kuwe. Inene wena useNdleleni ethe Tye
  43,44,"Inene yona (i’Kur’ân) iyinkumbuzo kuwe nabantu bakho, yaye niza kubuzwa"
  43,45,Ke kaloku buza abo Sabathumela phambi kwakho ngabaThunywa beThu. Ingaba Sakha Senza abanye oothixo na ngaphandle koSozinceba
  43,46,"Kananjalo Thina Sathuma uMûsâ nemiqondiso yeThu kuFir’awn nobukumkani bakhe, ke kaloku wathi (uMûsâ): “Inene mna ndingumthunywa weNkosi yamaphakade.”"
  43,47,"Kodwa wathi esakufika nemiqondiso yeThu, ngoko nangoko bahleka"
  43,48,Ke kaloku akukho mqondiso eSababonisa wona owawungemkhulwanga kunobesele Sibabonise wona8 (ngaphammbili kunawo) Sabahlasela ngesibetho ke khona ukuze babuyele ngenguquko
  43,49,"Ke kaloku bathi kuMûsâ: “Hini na wena menzi wemilingo cela eNkosini yakho ngoko Ikuthembise ngako. Inene thina siya kuba ngabakhokelelekileyo9.”"
  43,50,"Kodwa Sithi Sisakusisusa isibetho kubo, balaphule ngoko nangoko ilizwi labo (lesithembiso)"
  43,51,"Ke kaloku uFir’awn wakhwaza ebantwini bakhe; wathi: “Hini na bantu bam, ubukumkani baseYiputa asibobam na, nale milambo impompoza phantsi kwam, kanti aniboni na"
  43,52,"Okanye ayindim ongcono kunaye na lo (uMûsâ) ongento yanto, engakwazi nakucacisa (nto)"
  43,53,Kutheni ke kungabekwanga zacholo zagolide phezu kwakhe okanye eze ehamba kunye neengelosi?”
  43,54,"Wabaqhatha ke abantu bakhe, (uFir’awn) nabo bamthobela, inene bona babengabantu ababe nendelelo bengenantobeko (kuAllâh)"
  43,55,"Ke kaloku ukuSenza kwabo umsindo, Sathabatha impindezelo kubo, Sabatshonisa emanzini bonke"
  43,56,Kananjalo Sabenza baba sisibonelo nomzekelo kubantu abasezayo
  43,57,"Ke kaloku xa unyana kaMaryam wenziwa umzekelo, abantu bakuni bakhawulezisa bahleka ngokuvakalayo"
  43,58,"Ke kaloku bathi: “Ingaba ngabethu na oothixo abangcwele okanye nguye (uYesu)” (oku)11babengakuthetheli (kufanisa) ngaphandle kokwenzela impikiswano (njee) eneneni bona ngabantu abathanda impikiswano"
  43,59,"Yena (u’Isâ) wayengeyonto yimbi ngaphandle kokuba sisiCaka eSathulula uBabalo phezu kwaso, yaye Samenza waba ngumzekelo (omhle) kuBantwana bakwaSirayeli"
  43,60,"Ke kaloku ukuba Sasithandile ngeSenza (endaweni yenu nina bantu) iingelosi emhlabeni, zilandelelana (ezinye emva kwezinye)"
  43,61,"Inene yena (u’Isâ) uya kuba (ngumqondiso) wokwaziwa kweYure, ngoko ke wena ungabi nakuthandabuza ngayo, landela Mna. Le yiNdlela ethe Tye"
  43,62,"Kananjalo ungavumeli uShaytân akuphambukise. Inene, yena kuwe ulutshaba olucacileyo"
  43,63,"Ke kaloku ekufikeni kuka’Isâ nemiqondiso ecacileyo, wathi: “Mna ndize kuni nobulumko, nokuza kunicacisela ngeminye iimibandela eniphikisana ngayo ngoko ke yoyikani uAllâh nindithobele"
  43,64,"Inene uAllâh yiNkosi yam, ekwayiNkosi yenu. Khonzani Yena ke, le yiNdlela ethe Tye.”"
  43,65,"Kodwa zona iimvaba zaya zaba ziintlaba zahlukane phakathi kwazo (akwabikho kuvumelana), Ngoko ke Yeha ke esohlwayweni seMini ebuhlungu kwabo benza ubugwenxa"
  43,66,Ingaba balindele (nto yimbi) na ngaphandle kweYure eza kubafikela bengaqondi
  43,67,Abahlobo abakhulu ngaloo Mini baya kuba ziintshaba omnye komnye ngaphandle kwabenzi bokulungileyo
  43,68,"(Abo uAllâh Aya kuthi kubo): “Hini na zicaka zaM akukho koyika kuya kubakho malunga nani ngayo le Mini, ningayi kunxunguphala nakunxunguphala"
  43,69,(Nina) nakholwayo kwiiVesi zeThu naba ngamaMuslim
  43,70,"Ngenani ePaladesi, nina nabafazi benu nigcobile"
  43,71,"Okuya kuhanjiswa phakathi kwabo zizitya neendebe zegolide. Phakathi kuzo apho iya kuba kuko konke okunqwenelwa ngumphefumlo nokuchulumancisa amehlo, yaye niya kuhlala apho naphakade"
  43,72,Leyo ke yiPaladesi enenzelwe ukuba ziindlalifa zayo ngenxa yoko (kuzizenzo ezilungileyo) nakwenzayo
  43,73,Okwenu apho ziziqhamo ezininzi eniya kudla kuzo
  43,74,"Inene zona izaphula-mthetho ziya kuba sesohlwayweni, zihlale apho ngonaphakade"
  43,75,"(Isohlwayo eso) asiyi kuvunyelwa sithothe kubo, yaye bona apho baya kulahlekelwa lithemba"
  43,76,Ke kaloku ayiSithi ababenza ubugwenxa ngabo ngokwabo ababa ngabenzi bobugwenxa
  43,77,"Ke kaloku baza kuthi: “O, Mâlik12, khawenze iNkosi yakho Isenze sitshabalale (kube kanye)! ‘’Uya kuthi yena: “Inene niza kuhlala (ninjalo).”"
  43,78,Inene nina Sinizele nenyaniso kodwa uninzi lwenu luyichasile inyaniso
  43,79,Okanye banecebo abaliqulunqileyo na? NaThi Siqulunqa (eleThu) nje
  43,80,Okanye bacinga ukuba aSiziva iintetho zabo zasemakhusini? Ewe nje kwaye iziThunywa zeThu ziba kunye nabo zibhala
  43,81,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Ukuba uSozinceba Ebenonyana mna bendiya kuba ngowokuqala ukuba ngomnye wabanquli (bakhe loo nyana lowo).”"
  43,82,"Uzuko malube kwiNkosi yamazulu nomhlaba, iNkosi yeTrone, Engentla (lee) kwezo nto bazibalela (kuYo)"
  43,83,Ngoko ke bayeke (njalo) bancokole amampunge bazonwabise de bagagane neMini yabo leyo bathenjiswe ngayo
  43,84,"Kananjalo nguYe onguThixo (Okukuphela kwaKhe) ezulwini nasemhlabeni, yaye Yena nguSolwazi, uSobulumko"
  43,85,"Usikelelekile Yena loWo ulongamelo lwamazulu nomhlaba ilolwaKhe nako konke okuphakathi kwawo, Yena loWo ulwazi lweYure lukuYe, ekukuYe apho niza kubuyiselwa khona"
  43,86,"Abo babanqulayo ngaphandle kwaKhe (uAllâh) abanawo amandla okuthethelela; kuphela ngabo bangqinela inyaniso (abaya kunikwa igunya lokuthethelela), yaye bayazi"
  43,87,"Ke kaloku xa ubabuza okokuba ngubani na owabadalayo, ngokuqinisekileyo baza kuthi: “nguAllâh.’’ (ke ngoku) baqhathwe yintoni"
  43,88,"(UAllâh Uyayamkela) intetho yakhe (uMuhammad) ethi: “O Nkosi yam, inene aba bantu (ngabantu) abangakholwayo.”Ngoko ke wena zikhwebule kubo, uthi: “Makube luxolo.’’ Kodwa baza kwazi"
  43,89,"Ngoko ke suka kubo wena uthi: “Salâm” (makube luxolo) kodwa (kungekudala) baza kwazi"
  44,1,Hâ-Mîm
  44,2,NgeNcwadi ecacileyo
  44,3,"Inene Thina Sayithumela ngobusuku obusikelelekileyo, Singokulumkisa (uluntu)"
  44,4,Ngabo (obo busuku) kucaciswa into nganye icace gca (yahluke kwenye)
  44,5,"(Yonke)\tinto\tevela\tkuThi,\tinene\tThina\tSayithumela (uMthunywa)"
  44,6,"Owaba yinceba evela eNkosini uMlondolozi wakho, inene Yena nguSokuva nguSolwazi"
  44,7,"YiNkosi yamazulu nomhlaba noko kuphakathi kwawo, ukuba nifuna ukuqiniseka"
  44,8,"Akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaKhe; Yena Unika ubomi Enze ukufa. YiNkosi yakho, iNkosi yookhokho benu bokuqala"
  44,9,"Kodwa\t(abangakholwayo)\tbona\tbasekuthandabuzeni, bezonwabisa (ngokugculela nokubhoxa)"
  44,10,"Lindelani\tke\tiMini\tisibhakabhaka\tsiya\tkuzisa\tuMsi obonakalayo"
  44,11,Oya kugquma abantu. Esi sisohlwayo esibuhlungu
  44,12,"(Baya kuthi): “Nkosi yethu sisusele esi sohlwayo phezu kwethu, inene thina singamakholwa.’’"
  44,13,Uya kubakho njani umkhumbuzi kubo (ngaloo Mini)? Kube kubo kwakufike uMthunywa ocacileyo
  44,14,"Baza bona bamtshikilela besithi: “Ufundisiwe, ungumntu ophambanayo.’’"
  44,15,Inene Thina Siya kusisusa isohlwayo okwethutyana inene nina (bantu ndini) bangakholwayo niya kubuyela (ekungakholweni kwenu)
  44,16,"NgeMini eSiya kubetha ngohlaselo olukhulu, inene Thina Siya kuthabatha impindezelo"
  44,17,Ke kaloku sele Salinga abantu bakwaFir’awn ngaphambili kunabo yaye kwafika kubo uMthunywa ohloniphekileyo (uMûsâ)
  44,18,"(Esithi kuFir’awn): “Nikezela izicaka zika-Allâh kum, inene mna ndinguMthunywa othembekileyo kuwe,”"
  44,19,"(Esithi kananjalo kuye): “Musa ukukhukhumala kuAllâh. Inene mna ndize kuwe ndinegunya elicacileyo"
  44,20,Kananjalo mna ndaye ndacela ukhuseleko ngeNkosi yam EkwayiNkosi yakho kuba ngenanindixulube ngamatye
  44,21,Ke kaloku ukuba akundikholelwa ndiyeke ke.’’
  44,22,Ekugqibeleni wacela eNkosini yakhe (ekhalazela) ukuba ngenene aba yayingabantu abazizaphula-mthetho
  44,23,"(UAllâh) Wathi: “Wena (Mûsâ) phuma nezicaka zaM ngobusuku, inene niya kuleqwa"
  44,24,"Nilushiye ulwandle ngokuzolileyo, inene bona bangumkhosi oza kurhaxiswa.”"
  44,25,Kungakanani okwamasimi nemithombo abakushiya ngemva
  44,26,Nezityalo nezidiliya zexabiso
  44,27,Nobunewunewu ababonwatyiswe bubo
  44,28,Ngaloo ndlela abantu abangabanye baba ziindlalifa zazo (ezo zinto bazishiya ngemva)
  44,29,Kanti nawo amazulu nomhlaba azanga abalilele yaye abazanga banikwe xesha longezelelweyo
  44,30,Ke kaloku Sabasindisa abaNtwana bakwaSirayeli kwisohlwayo sehlazo
  44,31,Esivela kuFir’awn. Inene yena wayesisikhukhumali phakathi kwabagabadeli
  44,32,Inene Sabakhetha Thina bona (abaNtwana bakwaSirarayeli) ngolwazi ngaphezulu kumazwe onke
  44,33,Kananjalo Sabanika imiqondiso ekwakukho kuyo uvavanyo olucacileyo
  44,34,Inene aba bantu bangakholwayo bathi
  44,35,“Akukho nto injalo apha ngaphandle kokufa kokuqala yaye asizi kuphinda sivuswe
  44,36,Buyiselani ookhokho bethu (ebomini) kaloku ukuba nithetha inyaniso.”
  44,37,Ingaba ngabo abangcono okanye ngabantu baseTuba nabo babengaphambili kunabo? Sabatshabalalisa ke Thina (ngokuba) inene bona babezizaphula-mthetho
  44,38,Ke kaloku Asizanga Sidale amazulu nomhlaba noko kungaphakathi kuwo Siwadalela indlalo
  44,39,Asizanga Siwadale ngaphandle (kokuwadalela) inyaniso kodwa uninzi lwabo alwazi
  44,40,Inene iMini yoMgwebo lixesha elityunjelwe bona bonke
  44,41,"IMini apho kungayi kubakho sizalwana siya kunceda esinye isizalwana, bengayi kuncedwa nakuncedwa"
  44,42,"Ngaphandle kwabo bakholwayo uAllah Anenceba kubo.Yena nguSobunganga, uSozinceba"
  44,43,Inene wona umthi weZa’kkûm
  44,44,Uya kuba kukutya kwabenzi bezono
  44,45,"Unjenge-oli emdaka, ebila ngaphakathi eziswini"
  44,46,Njengamanzi abilayo atshisayo
  44,47,"(Kuya kuthiwa kumntu ongumoni): “Mbambeni nimrhuqele esazulwini soMlilo wesiHogo"
  44,48,Nize nigalele phezu kwentloko yakhe isohlwayo samanzi abilayo.”
  44,49,"(Kuya kuthiwa): “Ngcamla ke, wena ungumhlonitshwa, obekekileyo"
  44,50,Inene oku koko nanidla ngokukuphika.”
  44,51,"Inene, abenzi bokulungileyo baya kuba sendaweni yokhuseleko"
  44,52,Phakathi eMiyezweni nemithombo
  44,53,"Bambathe(izambatho)zesilikaesulungekileyonehonjisiweyo, bejongene"
  44,54,"(Kuya kuba njalo) Yaye Siya kubatshatisa neeHûrin’ayn1. Ezinamehlo amakhulu, athandekayo"
  44,55,Bayakubizaaphonayiphinaintloboyesiqhamobeseluxolweni naselukhuselekweni
  44,56,"Abasayi kuze bafe apho ngaphandle kokufa kokuqala (kweli hlabathi), yaye Yena Uya kubasindisa entuthumbeni yoMlilo odwanguzayo"
  44,57,NjengobuBele obuvela eNkosini yakho! Oko kuya kuba yimpumelelo enkulu
  44,58,Inene le (‘Kur’ân) Siyenze yalula elwimini lwakho khona ukuze ukhumbule
  44,59,Linda ke (Muhammad) nabo oku kwabo balindile
  45,1,"Hâ, Mîm"
  45,2,"Ukutyhilwa\rkweNcwadi\t(i’Kur’ân)\rkuvela\rkuAllâh,\ruSobunganga, uSobulumko"
  45,3,Inene emazulwini nasemhlabeni kukho imiqondiso kwabakholwayo
  45,4,Ke kaloku ekudalweni kwenu noko Akuthe saa kuzizidalwa ezinyakazayo kuyimiqondiso kubantu abaqinisekileyo (elukholweni)
  45,5,"Nasekuphumzaneni kobusuku nemini nakoko uAllâh Akuthumele phantsi kuvela esibhakabhakeni kusisixhaso (imvula) Anika ngaso ubomi emhlabeni emveni kokuba ubungenabomi, nasekukhokeleleni (kwaKhe) umoya, kukho imiqondiso kubantu abaqiqayo"
  45,6,Ezi ziiVesi zika-Allâh ESizicengceleza kuwe ngenyaniso. Ke ngoko yiyiphi (enye) ingxelo Emva kweka-Allah neeVesi zaKhe abaza (kude) bakholwe kuyo
  45,7,Yeha kuye nawuphi na umoni olixoki
  45,8,"Ozivayo iiVesi zika-Allâh zicengcelezwa kuye, aze aqhubeke nokuba nenkukhumalo abe ngathi akazivanga. Mnike iindaba ezivuyisayo ke ngoko zesohlwayo esibuhlungu"
  45,9,Kananjalo xa esazi nokuba yintoni na ngeeVesi zeThu uyazigculela (enze intlekisa ngazo). Okwabo (banjalo) sisohlwayo esilihlazo
  45,10,Phambi kwabo sisiHogo noko bakusebenzelayo akuyi kubanceda nto konke-konke noko bakuthathayo (bakunqulayo) ngaphandle koAllâh bekwenza abakhuseli babo. Yaye baya kufumana isohlwayo esikhulu
  45,11,Le ‘Kur’ân sisiKhokelo. Abo baya bangakholwa kwiiVesi zeNkosi yabo baya kufumana isohlwayo esiluhlobo olubi kanobom
  45,12,"NguAllâh Owanilulamisela ulwandle khona ukuze iinqanawa zihambe kulo ngomyalelo waKhe kwanokuba nifune uBubele baKhe, hleze nibe nombulelo"
  45,13,Kananjalo Unilulamisele okusemazulwini nokusemhlabeni konke kuvela kuYe. Inene kuko oko kukho imiqondiso kubantu abacingisisayo
  45,14,Yithi (Muhammad) kwabo bakholwayo kufanelekile ukuba babaxolele abo bangazilindelanga iiNtsuku zika- Allâh (zempindezelo) ukuze Abuyekeze abantu ngoko bakusebenzelayo
  45,15,"“Nabani na owenza isenzo esilungileyo, usenzela (usindiso) lomphefumlo wakhe, nalowo wenza okungcolileyo ukwenza ngokuchasene nawo (umphefumlo wakhe). Ukanti kuseNkosini yenu apho niza kubuyela khona.”"
  45,16,"Ke kaloku inene Sabanika isiBhalo aBantwana bakwaSirayeli (nenqobo) yokugweba nobuProfeti, Sabanika nezinto ezilungileyo, Sakhetha bona ngaphezulu kwendalo yonke"
  45,17,"Sabanika nemiqondiso ecacileyo kumbandela (wenkolo). Ke kaloku abazanga babe neyantlukwano de kwaba semva kokufika kolwazi kubo ngenxa yomona, nentiyano phakathi kwabo. Inene iNkosi wena landela yona, ungalandeli iminqweno yabo bangazi nto"
  45,18,"Saza Sabeka wena ke (Muhammad), eNdleleni eqhelekileyo mayela nombandela (wenkolo); ngoko ke omnye komnye. Kodwa Yena uAllâh nguMkhuseli wabenzi bokulungileyo"
  45,19,Inene bona asokuze bakuncede nto ngokuchasene noAllâh. Ke kaloku Inene abenzi bobubi bangabahlobo yakho Iza kugweba phakathi kwabo ngoMhla woVuko malunga noko babephikisana ngako
  45,20,"Le (‘Kur’ân) lukhanyiselo loluntu, isisiKhokelo nenceba kubantu abanengqiniseko (ngokholo lwabo)"
  45,21,Makube abo benza ukungcola bacinga ukuba Siza kubenza babe njengabo bakholwayo benza okulungileyo. (bacinga ukuba) baza kufaniswa kubomi babo nasekufeni kwabo? Okungcolileyo lugwebo1 lwabo
  45,22,"Ke kaloku uAllâh Wadala amazulu nomhlaba ngenyaniso khona ukuze umphefumlo ngamnye ubuyekezwe ngoko wakusebenzelayo, yaye abazi kwenziwa bugwenxa"
  45,23,"Umbonile na lowo uzithabathela iminqweno yakhe ayenze uthixo wakhe, uAllâh umyekele ekulahlekeni ngolwazi kwaye Ufake itywina ekuveni kwakhe nasentliziyweni yakhe, Waza Wabeka isigqumathelo phezu kokubona kwakhe? Ngubani ke onokumkhokela emva koAllâh? Ingaba aniyi kukhumbuzeka ke ngoko"
  45,24,"Ke kaloku bathi: “Akukho (bomi) ngaphandle (kobu) bomi bethu basemhlabeni; siyafa siphile, akukho nto isitshabalalisayo ngaphandle kwexesha.” Ukanti bona abanalwazi ngoko (bakuthethayo) bayaqikelela kuphela"
  45,25,"Naxa iiVesi zeThu zicengcelezwa kubo njengobungqina obucacileyo, ingxoxo yabo ibanye nje kukuthi: “Yiza nookhokho bethu kaloku ukuba uthetha inyaniso.”"
  45,26,"Yithi wena: “UAllâh Unenza niphile Aphinde Anenze nife kanti Usaya kunidibanisela iMini yoVuko, ekungekho ntandabuzo ngayo kodwa uninzi lwabantu alwazi"
  45,27,"Ke kaloku loluka-Allâh ulongamelo lwamazulu nomhlaba. Mhla iYure ifika, ngaloo Mini amaxoki aya kulahlekelwa"
  45,28,"Ke kaloku uya kubona iintlanga zonke ziguqa (zisoyika). Uhlanga ngalunye luya kubizelwa kokubhaliweyo kwalo (luxelelwe okokuba): “NaMhla uza kubuyekezwa ngoko wakusebenzelayo"
  45,29,Lo mbhalo weThu uthetha ngawe ngenyaniso. Inene Thina Sasikubhala konke owawukwenza.’’
  45,30,"Ngoko ke abo bakholwayo, benza izenzo ezilungileyo iNkosi yabo Iya kubangenisa encebeni yaYo. Oko kuko okuyinzuzo ecacileyo"
  45,31,"Kodwa bona abo baye bangakholwa (kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Azizanga zicengcelezwe na iiVesi zeThu kuni, kodwa nasuka nina nakhukhumala, naba ngabantu abazizaphula- mthetho"
  45,32,"Kananjalo xa kwakusithiwa (kuni): “Inene isithembiso sika- Allâh siyinyaniso neYure (iyeza) akukho kuthandabuza ngayo,’’ nathi nina: “Asiyazi ukuba yintoni na iYure. Siyaqikelela nje uqash-qash, yaye asanelisekanga (yingcaciso yayo).’’"
  45,33,Ke kaloku iziphumo ezingcolileyo zoko bakwenzayo ziya kubonakala kubo yaye baya kurhangqelwa koko babekugculela
  45,34,"Kuya kuthiwa kubo: “NaMhlanje Siya kulibala ngani njengoko nani nalibalayo ngendibano yale Mini yenu, yaye indawo yokubalekela kwenu nguMlilo, kwaye akuyi kubakho bancedi kuni"
  45,35,"Oko kwaba ngenxa yokuba nathabatha iiVesi zika- Allâh njengento yokuhlekisa, yaye ubomi basemhlabeni baniqhatha.’’ Ke kaloku ngaloo Mini abayi kukhutshwa kuwo (uMlilo) bengayi kucelwa ukuba bazicengezelele (kuAllâh)"
  45,36,"Ngoko ke iindumiso mazibe kuAllâh, iNkosi yamazulu nomhlaba, iNkosi yamaphakade"
  45,37,"BobaKhe (bonke) ubukhulu emazulwini nasemhlabeni, yaye nguSobunganga, nguSobulumko"
  46,1,Hâ - Mîm
  46,2,"Ukutyhilwa kweNcwadi i’Kur’ân kuvela kuAllâh, uSobunganga, uSobulumko"
  46,3,"ASiwadalanga amazulu nomhlaba nokuphakathi kwawo ngaphandle kwenyaniso, yaye (Siwadalele) ixesha elimisiweyo kodwa abo bangakholwayo koko balunyukiswa ngako bayakufulathela"
  46,4,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Nibajongile phofu abo nibanqulayo ngaphandle koAllâh? Khanindiboniseni abakudalileyo komhlaba: okanye mhlawumbi babe nobuhlulelane (ekudalweni) kwamazulu? Ndiziseleni isibhalo (esatyhilwa) ngaphambili kunesi (i’Kur’ân) okanye intwana (esaseleyo) yolwazi, ukuba nithetha inyaniso.”"
  46,5,Ngubani olahleke ngaphezulu kunalowo unqula abo bangekhe bamphendule ngaphandle koAllâh de kube yiMini yoVuko1 babe bona ngonqulo olo lwabo bengenalwazi
  46,6,"Xa abantu behlanganiswe ndawonye (ngaloo Mini), abo (babenqulwa) baya kuba ziintshaba kubo, yaye baya kuba ngabaphiki bokunqulwa kwabo"
  46,7,"Naxa iiVesi zeThu zicengcelezwa kubo njengobungqina obucacileyo, abo bangakholwayo bathi inyaniso isakuba ifikile kubo: “Lo ngumlingo ocacileyo.”"
  46,8,"Makube mhlawumbi bathi: “Uyiqambe ngokwakhe?” Yithi: “Ukuba ndiyiqambe ngokwam nina aniyi kuba nawo (amandla okundikhusela) ngokuchasene noAllâh. Yena nguYena ukwazi kakuhle enikwenzayo. Wanele Yena ukuba Abe liNgqina phakathi kwam nani, yaye nguMxoleli uSozinceba.”"
  46,9,"Yithi: “Andifani na nabemveli phakathi kwabaThunywa? Kanti ke mna andikwazi okuza kwenzeka kum okanye kuni. Mna ndilandela okutyhilwe kum kuphela, yaye mna andinto yimbi ngaphandle kokuba nguMlumkisi.”"
  46,10,"Yithi: “Niyaqonda na okokuba ukuba yona (i’Kur’ân) ibivela kuAllâh naze nina anakholwa kuyo lo gama ingqina phakathi kwaBatwana bakwaSirayeli langqinayo kwinto efana nayo (i’Kur’ân) laza lakholwa lona lo gama nina nikhukhumele?” Inene uAllâh Akabakhokeli abenzi bobubi"
  46,11,"Kananjalo abo bangakholwayo bathi kwabo bakholwayo “Ukuba ngaba (i’Kur’ân) ibilungile, ngebengasandulelanga2 kuyo” ke kaloku xa bengakhokelekekanga yiyo bathi: “Obu bubuxoki bakudala.”"
  46,12,Ke kaloku ngaphambili kunayo yayisisiTyhilelo sikaMûsâ esasisisiKhokelo nenceba. Le ke yiNcwadi engqinayo ngolwimi lwesiArabhu ukulumkisa abo benze ubugwenxa ibe ziindaba ezivuyisayo kubenzi bokulungileyo
  46,13,"Inene abo bathi: “INkosi yethu nguAllâh, baza bahlala beseNdleleni elungileyo, akuyi kubakho koyika ngokuphathelene nabo, bengayi kuxhalaba"
  46,14,"AbongamadlelaneePaladesi:bayakuhlalaaphongonaphakade njengomvuzo (wabo) ngenxa yoko bakwenzayo"
  46,15,"Kananjalo emntwini Siyalele impatho elungileyo kubazali. Unina wamthwala kanzima wamzala kanzima emva kokummitha nokumlumla iinyanga ezingamashumi amathathu3 (uye akhule) ade afikelele kwixabiso lokubhadla ade afikelele nakwixabiso lokuba neminyaka engamashumi amane, athi: “Nkosi yam ndenze ndibe nombulelo ngoBabalo lwaKho Owandenzela lona nabazali bam, (undenze) ndisebenze ubulungisa Oya kubamkela Wena, Undenzele nenzala engamalungisa. Inene mna ndiguqukele kuWe yaye mna ndingomnye wamaMuslim.”"
  46,16,"Bona bangabo kubo Siya kwamkela ezona zilungileyo kwizenzo zabo, Singazihoyi izenzo zabo ezigwenxa. (baya kuba) phakathi kwabemi basePaladesi isithembiso senyaniso, abathenjiswe ngaso"
  46,17,"Kodwa lowo uthi kubazali bakhe: “Uff4 kuni, nindithembisa ukuba ndiza kuphinda ndivuswe (ekufeni) lo gama izizukulwana ezingaphambili kunam sele zadlulayo?” Babe bona (abazali bakhe) bethandazela ukufumana uncedo kuAllâh (besithi kunyana lowo wabo): “Yeha kuwe! Kholwa! Inene isithembiso sika-Allâh siyinyaniso.” Kodwa athi yena, “Akunto yimbi oku ngaphandle kokuba ziintsomi zabantu bakudala"
  46,18,Abo (banjalo) ngabo ilizwi (lommiselo) liye lehla (phezu kwabo) abaya kuba phakathi kwezizwe ezagqithayo ngaphambili kunabo zeejinni nabantu. Inene bonke baba ngabalahlekelwa
  46,19,"Kubo bonke kukho amanqanaba (omvuzo nawesohlwayo) ngoko bakwenzayo, yaye kunjalo khona ukuze Ababuyekeze ngokugcweleyo ngezenzo zabo kwaye abayi kwenziwa bugwenxa"
  46,20,"NgeMini abo bangazanga bakholwe beya kusondezwa eMlilweni (kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Nabufinca bonke ubumnandi benu ngethuba nanisemhlabeni, nabonwabela, Ke naMhla niya kubuyekezwa ngesohlwayo sehlazo ngokuba nanikhukhumele emhlabeni ngokungekho lungelweni ngenxa yokuba naninendelelo, ningenantobeko.”"
  46,21,"Yabona, (uHûd) umzalwana wama’Ad xa walumkisa abantu bakubo kwinginqi yase Al-Ah‘kâf, ukanti abalumkisi (abaninzi) babesele bagqitha ngaphambili kunaye nasemva kwakhe (besithi): “Musani ukunqula nto ngaphandle koAllâh. Inene mna ndiyanoyikisela kwisohlwayo seMini embi kunene.”"
  46,22,"Bathi bona: “Ingaba uze kusiwexula na koothixo bethu? Khawuze ke noko usithembisa ngako ukuba uthetha inyaniso.”"
  46,23,"Wathi yena: “Ulwazi lokwenzeka kwako (oko ndinithembisa ngako) lukuAllâh kuphela, mna ndinichazela endikuthunyiweyo; kodwa ndinibona ningabantu abaziphatha ngobudenge.”"
  46,24,"Ke kaloku ukukubona kwabo (oko babethenjiswe ngako5) kunjengelifu elisondela kwiintili zabo, bathi: “Eli lilifu elisizela nemvula!” (UHûd wathi): “Nakanye (oku) koko beningasenamonde ngako, ngumoya ekukho isohlwayo esibuhlungu kuwo.”"
  46,25,"Esitshabalalisa into yonke ngomyalelo weNkosi yaso, baba njalo ke kwaza akwabikho nto yaphinda yabonwa ngaphandle kwamabhodlo abo, Sibabuyekeza kanjalo ke abantu abangabaphuli-mthetho"
  46,26,"Ke kaloku Sabamisela (emhlabeni) ngendlela eSinganimiselanga ngayo nina, yaye Sabenzela ukuva nokubona neentliziyo (ingqiqo). Kodwa ukuva nokubona kwabo neentliziyo zabo azizanga zibancede nto xa babesala iiVesi zika-Allâh; yaye baye bagutyungelwa koko babekugculela"
  46,27,Kananjalo Sele Sakutshabalalisa okuningqongileyo (kwezo) zixeko yaye Siyenze ayafana imiqondiso khona ukuze abantu babe nokubuyela (elukholweni)
  46,28,"Kwakutheni ke abo babebathatha njengoothixo bokubasondeza (kuAllâh) bangabancedi kaloku? Nakanye, babashiya enyanyeni (ngokuba) kakade yayibubuxoki obo nomqambo (njee ongenasihlahla)"
  46,29,"Yabona (Muhammad), Sathumela ngakuwe iijinni ezimbalwa, (ukuba zize) kuphulaphula i’Kur’ân. Ekuyiphulaphuleni kwazo zathi (zithetha zodwa): “Phulaphulani nithi cwaka.” Yakugqitywa (ukucengcelezwa i’Kur’ân) zabuyela kwabakuzo njengabalumkisi"
  46,30,"Zathi: “Mawethu, inene thina sive (ucengcelezo) lweNcwadi etyhilwe emva kwekaMûsâ ingqina okwaba ngaphambili kunayo okukhokelela enyanisweni nakwiNdlela ethe Tye.”"
  46,31,"Mawethu, mhoyeni ummemezi (uMthunywa) ka-Allâh nikholwe futhi kuYe (uAllâh), Uya kunixolela izono zenu, Anikhusele kwisohlwayo esibuhlungu"
  46,32,Lowo ungasabeliyo kummemezi ka-Allâh akayi kumenza Asilele (uAllâh nangantoni na) emhlabeni yaye (loo mntu) akayi kuba namkhuseli ngaphandle kwaKhe. Abo (banjalo) basekulahlekeni okucacileyo.”
  46,33,"Ababoni na ukuba uAllâh Owadala amazulu nomhlaba Akasileli ekuwadaleni, Uyakwazi ukunika ubomi kwabafileyo? Ewe nje! Yena Unamandla ngaphezulu kweento zonke"
  46,34,"Ke\tkaloku\tngeMini\tabo\tbangakholwayo\tbesondezwa eMlilweni (kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Asiyonyani na le?” baya kuthi bona: “Ewe, (yiyo sifunga) ngeNkosi yethu.” Uya kuthi Yena (uAllâh): “Ngcamlani isohlwayo ke kuba nina naye anakholwa.”"
  46,35,"Ngokokeyibanomonde,njengabobabezimiselekubaThunywa ungaphelelwa ngumonde kananjalo ngokuphathelene nabo (bangakholwayo). Iya kuba ngathi (ngaloo) Mini bathenjiswe ngayo azanga baba semhlabeni ngaphandle kweYure yemini. Sisaziso (ke esi). Kodwa ingaba ukhona oza kutshatyalaliswa ngaphandle komntu odelelayo nongenantobeko"
  47,1,"Abo bangakholwayo baze bathintela (abantu) ukuba bangangeni eNdleleni ka-Allâh, Uya kuzilahla izenzo zabo"
  47,2,"Ke bona abo bakholwayo, benze izenzo ezilungileyo, bakholwe nakoko kutyhilwe kuMuhammad yaye kuyinyaniso evela eNkosini yabo, Yona Iya kuguzula izenzo zabo ezingendawo kubo, Ibaphuculele imeko yabo"
  47,3,Oko kungenxa yokuba abo bangakholwayo balandela ubuxoki kanti bona abo bakholwayo balandela inyaniso evela eNkosini yabo. Ubenzela kanjalo ke uAllâh abantu imfaniso yabo
  47,4,"Ngoko ke xa niqubisana nabo bangakholwayo (edabini) bageceni iintamo zabo nide nibathuthumbise ngokubabulala, emva koko nigcine abathinjwa babo nize ukuba niyathanda nibenzele inceba okanye nibakhulule ngentlawuliso de imfazwe yothule imigodlo yayo1. Lowo (ngumyalelo ka- Allâh). Kananjalo ukuba uAllâh Ebethandile ngezithabathele impindezelo ngokwaKhe kodwa Uye (Wayalela umzabalazo wezixhobo) ukuvavanya abanye ngabanye. Kananjalo abo babulewe eNdleleni ka-Allâh"
  47,5,Yena Uya kubakhokela Aphucule imeko yabo
  47,6,Abangenise ePaladesi Ayenze yazeke kubo
  47,7,"Hini na nina bakholwayo, ukuba nincedisa uAllâh Uya kunincedisa nani, Amilisele iinyawo zenu ngokuqinileyo. (uAllâh) Akasokuze azisingele phantsi izenzo zabo"
  47,8,Kodwa abo bangakholwayo okwabo yimbandezelo kwaye Yena Uya kuyisingela phantsi imisebenzi yabo
  47,9,"Oko kungenxa yokuba bekuchasile oko uAllâh Akutyhilileyo, ngoko ke Wenze izenzo zabo azabi nto yanto"
  47,10,Kanti abahamba-hambanga na elizweni babone ukuba saba njani na isiphelo sabo babandulelayo? uAllâh Watshabalalisa (yonke into) phezu kwabo ukanti (okulindele) abakholwayo (ikwa) yinto ekwanjengaleyo
  47,11,OkokungenxayokubauAllâhnguMkhuseliwabobakholwayo kwanokuba abangakholwayo abanamkhuseli
  47,12,"Inene uAllâh Uya kubangenisa abo bakholwayo, benza imisebenzi elungileyo eMiyezweni ekumpompoza imilambo, kodwa bona abo bangakholwayo bayazonwabisa batye okwezilwanyana ezitya ingca kanti uMlilo iya kuba likhaya labo"
  47,13,"Zingaphi izixeko ezaziluqilima kunesixeko senu (iMakkah) (sixeko eso saseMakkah) sakugxothayo wena (Muhammad)? Sazitshabalalisa ke Thina: yaye akuzanga kubekho mncedi wazo (ezo zixeko)"
  47,14,"Ingaba abo basebungqineni obucacileyo obuvela eNkosini yabo bayafana nabo ukungcola kwezenzo zabo kwenziwe kwanomtsalane kubo, balandela iminqweno yabo"
  47,15,"Ingaba inkcazo yePaladesi, leyo abakholwayo bathenjiswe ngayo ekumpompoza imilambo emanzi wayo angaphithikezwanga, imilambo yobisi encasa yawo ingaguqukiyo, imilambo yewayini emnandi kwabo bayiselayo, nemilambo yobusi obuhlambulukileyo, abaza kufumana kuyo zonke iintlobo zeziqhamo noxolelo lwezono oluvela eNkosini yabo, yafana na neyabo baza kuhlala eMlilweni ngonaphakade benikwa amanzi atshisayo aza kubuxula amathumbu abo"
  47,16,"Phakathi kwabo (Muhammad) kukho abo bakuphulaphulayo, de bemke kuwe, bathi kwabo babenikwe ulwazi: “Yintoni le agqiba ukuyitsho ngoku?” Abo ngabo uAllâh atywine iintliziyo zabo, abalandela iminqweno yabo (engendawo)"
  47,17,Ke bona abo bakhokelelekileyo Uyabongezelelela isiKhokelo Abanike ubulungisa babo
  47,18,Ingaba balinde nto yimbi na ngaphandle kokuba iYure isuke ibafikele bengalindelanga? Kodwa sele zifikile kakade iimpawu ezithile (zayo) Iya kunceda ntoni inkumbulo2 yabo xa sele ifikile
  47,19,"Yazi ke wena okokuba akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle koAllâh, ucele netarhu ngezono zakho, nangezamakholwa namakholwakazi. Kwaye uAllah Unolwazi ngentshukumo yakho nendawo yakho yokuphumla"
  47,20,"Abo bakholwayo bathi: “Kutheni kungekho Sûrah ithunyelweyo kodwa isakuthunyelwa iSûrah echanekileyo, nokulwa kukhankanyiwe kuyo, uye ubabone abo bantliziyo zabo zinesifo (sobuhanahanisi) bekujonge (ndlaa) oku komntu ofunyenwe kukufa. Ke kaloku okona bekuya kubalungela ngakumbi bona"
  47,21,"Yintobeko namazwi alungileyo, naxa umbandela (wokulwa) ubusele usekiwe, ukuba bebenyanisekile kuAllâh, bekuya kuba ngcono kubo oko"
  47,22,"Ingaba nina ukuba mhlawumbi beninokujibilika, beniza kwenza ubutshinga emhlabeni niqhawule amaqhina okuzalana (nezizalwana zenu)"
  47,23,"Abo (benza oko) ngabo uAllâh Abaqalekisileyo, ngoko ke Ubenze baba nobuthulu, Wabaphanyaza nokubona kwabo"
  47,24,"Kanti abayicamgcisisi na i’Kur’ân, okanye kukho izitshixo ezintliziyweni zabo"
  47,25,Inene abo baye batyibilika babuyela (ekungakholweni) emva kokuba isiKhokelo besele sifikile kubo uShaytân ubarhwebeshile walolula nethemba labo (lobuxoki)
  47,26,"Oku kungenxa yokuba bathi kwabo bakuchasileyo oko uAllâh Akutyhilileyo (i’Kur’ân): “Siya kunithobela kwinxalenye yombandela.” Kodwa Yena uAllâh Uyayazi imfihlelo yabo"
  47,27,"Kazi okokuba kuya kuba njani na xa iingelosi zibathabatha (ngethuba) lokufa kwabo, zibabetha ebusweni babo nasemiqolo yabo"
  47,28,"Oko kungenxa yokuba baye balandela oko kwavusa umsindo ka-Allâh bachasa oko kuMkholisayo, Waza Wazenza zabubuvuvu izenzo zabo"
  47,29,Makube mhlawumbi abo bantliziyo zabo zinesifo bacinga ukuba uAllâh Akayi kuziveza elubala (iimbono) zabo eziyinkcaso
  47,30,"KananjaloukubabeSithandabeSingabavezakuwe, yayeubuza kubazi ngophawu lwabo; kodwa uza kubazi ngemvakalo zwi yentetho yabo. Kwaye uAllâh uyazazi izenzo zenu"
  47,31,"Ke kaloku Siya kunivavanya de bacace abo bazabalazela (iNdlela ka-Allâh) phakathi kwenu nabanomonde, yaye Siya kuyicikida imibandela yenu"
  47,32,"Inene abo bangakholwayo, bathintela (abanye) eNdleleni ka- Allâh, baphikise uMthunywa (uMuhammad) emva kokuba isikhokelo sicacile kubo asokuze bamonzakalise uAllâh, kwaye Yena Uya kusuka Enze izenzo zabo zibe yinto engento"
  47,33,"Hini na nina bakholwayo, thobelani uAllâh, nithobele uMthunywa ningatshitshisi izenzo zenu (ngokungamthobeli)"
  47,34,"Inene abo bangakholwayo, bathintela abanye eNdleleni ka- Allâh baze bafe besengabangakholwayo Akasokuze abaxolele uAllâh"
  47,35,Ngoko ke ningatyhafi nicele ukuba makube luxolo (imfazwe iphele) lo gama inini abangentla; kwaye uAllâh Ukunye nani Engasokuze Anibandezele umvuzo wezenzo zenu
  47,36,"Ubomi beli hlabathi lulonwabo (lobuxoki) yaye buya phambukisa. Kanti ke ukuba niyakholwa, noyike uAllâh, Yena Uya kuninika imivuzo yenu yaye Akayi kucela izinto zenu"
  47,37,"Ukanti ukuba Ebenokuzicela kuni, beniya kuzinkonya, yaye Ebeza kuyiveza elubala inkcaso yenu"
  47,38,"Aphakeninaningabobamenyelwaukubabanikele(ngamalizo) eNdleleni ka-Allâh kodwa phakathi kwenu kukho abo banobugqolo. Nabani na ke onobugqolo (abanjalo) banjalo ngokuchasene neziqu zabo. Yena uAllâh Akadingi nto ukanti nini abadingayo. Ke kaloku ukuba nithe natyibilika narhoxa eNdleleni, Yena Uya kwenza abanye abantu endaweni yenu bona ke abayi kuba njengani"
  48,1,Inene Thina Sikunikile wena (Muhammad) uloyiso olucacileyo
  48,2,"Nokuba uAllâh Uya kukuxolela izono zakho zamandulo nexesha elizayo, Agqibelelise uBabalo lwakhe kuwe, Akukhokelele eNdleleni ethe Tye"
  48,3,Nokuba uAllâh Uya kukunceda ngoncedo olumandla
  48,4,"NguYe Owathumela inzolo ezintliziyweni zamakholwa ukwenzela ukuba ongezeleleke ukholo phezu kokholo analo yaye yeka-Allâh imikhosi yamazulu nomhlaba kananjalo uAllah nguSolwazi, uSobulumko"
  48,5,"Kwanokuba Uya kungenisa amakholwa namakholwakazi eMiyezweni ekumpompoza imilambo ngaphantsi kwayo bahlale apho ngonaphakade, Abasusele izenzo zabo ezigwenxa kubo Oko ke yinzuzo enkulu kuAllâh"
  48,6,"Nokuba Uza kubohlwaya abahanahanisi nabahanahanisikazi, abakhonzi bezithixo nabakhonzazana bezithixo, nabo bacinga iingcinga ezingcolileyo ngoAllâh. Phezu kwabo kukho ishwangusha eliluhlobo olungcolileyo kwaye uAllâh Unomsindo ngokubhekisele kubo, Wabaqalekisa nokubaqalekisa, Wabalungiselela isiHogo, Hayi ukungcola kwesiphelo sohambo lwabo"
  48,7,"Ke kaloku yeka-Allâh imikhosi esemazulwini nasemhlabeni. Kananjalo uAllâh nguSobunganga, uSobulumko"
  48,8,"Inene wena, Sikuthumelele ukuba ube lingqina nomvakalisi weendaba ezivuyisayo noMlumkisi"
  48,9,"Kwanokuba nina nikholwe kuAllâh noMthunywa waKhe nimhloniphe nimenzele imbeko (uMuhammad), NiMzukise (uAllâh) ekuseni nangenjikalanga"
  48,10,"Inene abo benza isifungo sesibophelelo kuwe (Muhammad) bona enyanisweni benza isifungo sesibophelelo kuAllâh. ISandla sika-Allâh siphezu kwezandla zabo. Ke lowo waphula isithembiso sakhe, usaphula ngokuchasene nesiqu sakhe. Lowo uzalisekisa oko athembise ngako kuAllâh, (uAllâh) Uya kumnika umvuzo omkhulu"
  48,11,"Ke kaloku abo baye bashiyeke ngemva bangama-Arabhu asentlango, baza kuthi kuwe: “Iimpahla zethu neentsapho zethu ziye zasibambezela, ngoko ke wena sicelele itarhu (kuAllâh).” Bona bathetha ngamalwimi abo okungekho zintliziyweni zabo. Yithi: “Ngubani ongathintela uAllâh xa Enokuthi Athande ukuba uhlelwe kokuluncedo? Nakanye, uAllâh Ukwazi konke enikwenzayo"
  48,12,Kodwa nina nanicinga okokuba uMthunywa (uMuhammad) namakholwa asokuze baphinde babuyele kwiintsapho zabo kananjalo oko kwenziwa kwakuhle ezintliziyweni zenu. Nina nacinga iingcinga ezingcolileyo naza naba ngabantu abatshabalalayo.”
  48,13,Nabani na ongakholwanga kuAllâh nomthunywa waKhe (Muhammad) inene abangakholwanga sibalungiselele iDangatya
  48,14,"Loluka-Allah ulongamelo lwamazulu nomhlaba, Uxolela lowo Athande ukumxolela Ohlwaye lowo Athande ukumohlwaya. UAllâh nguMxoleli, uSozinceba"
  48,15,"Abo babeshiyeke ngemva baza kuthi xa nisiya kuthabatha ixhayelo; “Masinilandele nathi.” Banqwenela ukuguqula amazwi ka-Allâh. Yithi: “Aningekhe\tnisilandele. Sele\tEtsho njalo\tuAllâh kwangaphambili” Baya kuthi ke bona: “Nini nje abasimonelayo”\tkodwa\t(enyanisweni)\tbabengaqiqi\tnto ngaphandle kokuncinane"
  48,16,"Yithi ke kwabo babeshiyeke ngemva bangama-Arabhu asentlango:“Nizakubizwa(niqubisane) nabantuabanomkhosi onamandla (ngakumbi) niya kulwa nabo ke okanye bona bazinikele, (kuni) ngoko ke ukuba niyathobela uAllâh Uya kuninika umvuzo olungileyo; kodwa ukuba niyajibilika njengoko nanijibilikile ngaphambili, Uya kunohlwaya ngesohlwayo esibuhlungu.”"
  48,17,"Akukho tyala koyimfama, okanye kosisiqhwala okanye kogulayo (ngokushiyeka kwabo ngasemva) Nabani na ke othobela uAllâh noMthunywa waKhe Uya kumngenisa emiyezweni ekumpompoza imilambo ngaphantsi kwayo: kodwa lowo ujikayo emke Uya kumohlwaya ngesohlwayo esikhulu"
  48,18,"Inene uAllâh Wakholiseka ngamakholwa xa ayesenza isifungo sesibophelelo kuwe (Muhammad), phantsi komthi, kwaye Wayekwazi okusentliziyweni, Waza Wathulula inzolo nokwaneliseka komphefumlo phezu kwawo Wawavuza ngoloyisokazi olukhulu"
  48,19,"Kananjalo lininzi ixhayelo lemfazwe abaya kulithatha kwaye uAllâh nguSobunganga, uSobulumko"
  48,20,UAllâh Unithembise ixhayelo elininzi eniya kulithatha kwaye Anikhokelele eNdleleni ethe Tye
  48,21,"Kananjalo Unithembisenangolunye(uloyiso) eningekafikeleli kulo kodwa Yena uAllâh Sele eligubungele, kwaye uAllâh Ungentla kwezinto zonke"
  48,22,"Ke kaloku ukuba abo (bantu baseMakkah) bangakholwayo bebeza kunilwa, bebeza kunizela ngemiva (banibaleke). Bebengazi kufumana mkhuseli namncedisi"
  48,23,(Le)yiNdlelaemiselweyoka-Allâheyayikhonanangaphambili yaye awusokuze ufumane kuguquka eNdleleni ka-Allâh
  48,24,Kananjalo nguYe Owabamba izandla zabo ukuba zingafikeleli kuni nezandla zenu ukuba zingafikeleli kubo (ngexesha) laseMakkah emva kokuba Waye nenze naba nokuboyisa. UAllâh nguSokubona woko nikwenzayo
  48,25,"Bona (abantu baseMakkah) yayingabo ababengakholwa benithintela ukuba ningangeni eMasjid al-Harâm lo gama idini lomnikelo lalithintelekile ukuba lifikelele kwindawo yokunikelwa kwalo. Ke kaloku ukuba\tkwakungekho ngenxa yamakholwa namakholwakazi enaningawazi nina ukuba ningasuke niwanyathele (niwabulale) kwanokuba naniya kuhlelwa kukungaxabiseki ngenxa yabo ningazi ngenanivunyelwe ukuba ningene (eMakkah). (Oku kwaba njalo) khona ukuze uAllâh Angenise encebeni yaKhe lowo Athande ukumngenisa. Ukuba abakholwayo babengekho kunye nabo (eMakkah) ngesasibohlwayile abo bangakholwayo phakathi kwabo ngesohlwayo esibuhlungu"
  48,26,"Yabona! Abo bangakholwayo bathi besakuba nenkukhumalo nekratshi, inkukhumalo yemihla yokungazi, Yena uAllâh Wathulula ukuthozama phezu koMthunywa waKhe naphezu kwamakholwa, wayalela phezu kwawo ilizwi lokwenziwa kokulungileyo, yaye ayefanelekile lilo ilizwi elo yaye uAllâh nguSolwazi wezinto zonke"
  48,27,"Inene uAllâh Uza kuwufezekisa umbono wokwenyani Awawubonisa uMthunywa waKhe. Inene nina (maMuslim) niza kungena eMasjid al-Harâm, uAllâh Ethandile ngenene nangenyaniso, nichebe iintloko zenu, iinwele zenu ziphungulwe, ningoyiki bani. Yena (uAllâh) Wazi ebeningakwazi yaye Ucwangcise kwangaphambili kunoko uloyiso olukufuphi nolo (kungekudala)"
  48,28,"NguYe Owathumela uMthunywa nesiKhokelo nenkolo yenyaniso ukuba Ayibonakalise ngaphezulu kweenkolo zonke, yaye uAllâh liNgqina elaneleyo"
  48,29,"UMuhammad nguMthunywa ka-Allâh ukanti abo bakunye naye bangqwabalala kwabangakholwayo, banenceba phakathi kwabo (bodwa). Ubabona bequbuda (emthandazweni) befuna ubuBele buka-Allâh nokuthandwa nguYe. Uphawu lwabo lusebusweni babo (emabunzini) oluvela kumzila wokuqubuda. Yinkcazo yabo ke leyo ephuma kwiTorah, kanti inkcazo yabo kwiVangeli injengesityalo esivelisa iingcambu zaso, size sizomeleze ukuze zintshule ziqine zime ngeziqu zazo, zivuyise umlimi (wazo) khona ukuze (uAllâh) Abahlahlambise abangakholwayo. UAllâh Uthembise abo bakholwayo, benza izenzo ezilungileyo phakathi kwabo, ngoxolelo lwezono, nomvuzo omkhulu"
  49,1,"Hini na nina bakholwayo musani ukukhokela uAllâh noMthunywa waKhe (ngokuthabatha isigqibo), kananjalo moyikeni uAllâh, inene! UAllâh nguSokuva, nguSolwazi"
  49,2,"Hini na nina bakholwayo, musani ukuphakamisa amazwi enu abe ngentla kwelizwi loMprofeti (uMuhammad) okanye nikhwaze xa nithetha naye njengokukhwazana kwabanye benu, hleze izenzo zenu zibe yinto engento, nibe ningazi nina"
  49,3,"Inene abo bathoba amazwi abo phambi koMthunywa ka- Allâh bona bangabo iintliziyo zabo uAllâh Azivavanyele ubulungisa, okwabo luxolelo lwezono nomvuzo omkhulu"
  49,4,Inene abo bakukhwaza ngemva ezindlwini zabo uninzi lwabo abasebenzisi ngqiqo
  49,5,"Ukuba bebenokulinda ude uphume uze kubo, bekuya kuba kokona kulungileyo oko kubo. Kodwa uAllâh nguMxoleli uSozinceba"
  49,6,"Hini na nina bakholwayo, xa kufika kuni (umntu) oyiFâsi’k1 (esiza) nenkcazelo, phandani, kuba hleze nonzakalise abantu ningazi ngoko nikwenzileyo, nizisole"
  49,7,"Yazini into yokuba phakathi kwenu kukho uMthunywa ka- Allâh. Ukuba ngaba ebeza kuthobela nina ubukhulu becala, beniya kuba sebunzimeni, kodwa uAllâh Unibonelele ngokholo, Walwenza lwathandeka nasezintliziyweni zenu, Wenza kwathiyeka kuni ukungakholwa, indelelo, nokungabi nantobeko. Abo (banjalo) ngabona bakhokelelekileyo"
  49,8,(Obo) bubuBele obuvela kuAllâh noBabalo kwaye uAllâh nguSolwazi uSobulumko
  49,9,"Ke kaloku ukuba ngaba amaqela amabini angamakholwa ayalwa, yenzani uxolelwaniso phakathi kwawo omabini. Kodwa ukuba elinye kuwo lenza ugabadelo kwelinye, yilwani nelo lenza ugabadelo de libuyele emgaqweni ka- Allâh. Ukuba liyabuyela ke yenzani uxolelwaniso phakathi kwawo ngokusebulungiseni, (nani) nenze ngokobulungisa ngokuba uAllâh Uyabathanda abo banobulungisa"
  49,10,"Amakholwa wona ngabazalwana, ngoko ke yenzani uxolelaniso phakathi kwabazalwana benu. Noyike uAllâh kananjalo ukuze nizuze (ukwenzelwa) inceba"
  49,11,"Hini na nina bakholwayo, makungabikho bantu benza intlekisa ngabanye abantu, (kunokwenzeka) mhlawumbi (kuthi kanti) bona (aba kuhlekiswa ngabo) ngabona bangcono kunabo; kungabikho bafazi kananjalo abenza intlekisa (ngabanye) abafazi (kunokwenzeka) mhlawumbi (kuthi kanti) ngabo abangcono kunabo (bahlekayo). Kananjalo musani ukuthukana, ningabizani ngamagama eziqhulo ezikhubekisayo. Libi igama elisisiqhulo (elithetha) ububi emva kokuba (umntu amkele i-Islam) enokholo. Kananjalo lowo ungaguqukiyo ngabo banjalo ke abangabenzi bobubi"
  49,12,"Hini na nina bakholwayo kuphepheni ukukrokrela, inene, ezinye izikrokro zisisono. Kananjalo musani ukucuphana okanye nihlebane. Ingaba omnye apha kuni angathanda ukudla inyama yomntakwabo efile? Ningayonyanya. Yoyikani uAllâh ke; uAllâh nguMamkeli wenguquko, Unenceba"
  49,13,"Hini na bantu Sanidala ngendoda nomfazi Sanenza nazizizwe neentlanga khon’ukuze nazane. Oyena uhloniphekileyo phakathi kwenu ngulowo uMoyika kakhulu uAllâh. Inene uAllâh nguSolwazi, Owazi konke"
  49,14,"Ama-Arabhu asentlango athi: “Sikholiwe.” Yithi: “Anikhange (niqale) ukukholwa; qha nina yithani “Sizinikele (kwi-Islam) ngokuba ukholo alukangeni ezintliziyweni zenu. Kanti ukuba niyaMthobela uAllâh noMthunywa waKhe, Akayi kunibandezela nto ngezenzo zenu. Inene uAllâh nguMxoleli, nguSozinceba.”"
  49,15,"Amakholwa kuphela akholwa kuAllâh nakuMthunywa waKhe, aze emva koko angathandabuzi koko wona azabalaza eNdleleni ka-Allâh ngezinto zawo nobomi bawo. Abo ngabo banyanisekileyo"
  49,16,"Yithi: “Ingaba niza kuxelela uAllâh ngenkolo yenu lo gama uAllâh Esazi okusemazulwini nasemhlabeni, kananjalo uAllâh Unolwazi ngaphezulu kwezinto zonke"
  49,17,"Bacinga ukuba benzela wena uvelwano (Muhammad) ngokwamkela kwabo i-Islam. Yithi: “Musani ukuthabatha ukwamkela kwenu i-Islam njengovelwano kum. Ukusuka apho uAllâh Wenzela nina ukuba Anikhokelele elukholweni, ukuba ninenyaniso.”"
  49,18,"Inene, uAllâh Wazi (iinkalo) ezingabonwayo zamazulu nomhlaba. Kananjalo uAllâh Uyakubona oko nikwenzayo"